文本内容: An advanced autopainter preprogrammed with several paintjobs for airlocks. Use it on an airlock during or after construction to change the paintjob. Alt-Click to remove the ink cartridge.
翻译内容: 先进的自动喷漆器，预制了几种气闸的喷漆样式，当建造时气闸时或完成建造后在气闸上使用来改变喷漆样式，Alt+点击来取出墨盒。

文本内容: An airlock painter, reprogramed to use a different style of paint in order to apply decals for floor tiles as well, in addition to repainting doors. Decals break when the floor tiles are removed. Alt-Click to remove the ink cartridge.
翻译内容: 气闸涂手，进行了重编程使之除了可以在气闸上面喷涂以外，也同样可以在地板上喷出图案来，拆除地板时图案会消失，Alt+点击来取出墨盒

文本内容: An airlock painter, reprogramed to use a different style of paint in order to spray colors on floor tiles as well, in addition to repainting doors. Decals break when the floor tiles are removed. Alt-Click to change design.
翻译内容: 气闸涂手，进行了重编程使之除了可以在气闸上面喷涂以外，也同样可以在地板上喷出不同颜色的图案，拆除地板时图案会消失，Alt+点击来更换设计

文本内容: Used for repairing or building APCs.
Blueprints of the station. There is a \"Classified\" stamp and several coffee stains on it.
翻译内容: 空间站的蓝图，上面有一个 \"机密\" 印章和一些咖啡渍

文本内容: A digital copy of the station blueprints stored in your memory.
翻译内容: 存储在你内存中的数字版站点蓝图

文本内容: A folded bag designed for the storage and transportation of cadavers.
翻译内容: 一个折叠好的袋子，为运输和存储尸体而打造

文本内容: A folded bluespace body bag designed for the storage and transportation of cadavers.
翻译内容: 一个折叠好的袋子，为运输和存储大量尸体而打造

文本内容: A folded, reinforced bag designed to protect against exoplanetary environmental storms.
翻译内容: 一个折叠好的加固袋子，为了抵抗外星球的环境风暴而打造

文本内容: A folded, heavily reinforced, and insulated bag, capable of fully isolating its contents from external factors.
翻译内容: 一个折叠好的重型绝缘加固袋子，能够将其内容物与外环境完全隔离

文本内容: Intended for transport of prisoners through hazardous environments, this folded environmental protection bag comes with straps to keep an occupant secure.
翻译内容: 用于在危险环境中运送囚犯，这款折叠的环境保护袋拥有绑带来固定其乘员

文本内容: An alteration of Nanotrasen's environmental protection bag which has been used in several high-profile kidnappings. Designed to keep a victim unconscious, alive, and secured until they are transported to a required location.
翻译内容: 纳米传讯的环境保护袋的改良版，用于多起高调绑架案，旨在让其受害者保持昏迷，活着和固定，直到被运输至所需位置

文本内容: A bouquet of sunflowers, lilies, and geraniums. How delightful.
翻译内容: 一束向日葵，百合和天竺葵。令人欣快

文本内容: A bouquet of poppies. You feel loved just looking at it.
翻译内容: 一束罂粟花，你光是看着就感觉被爱着

文本内容: A bouquet of roses. A bundle of love.
A tool for cutting boxes, or throats.
翻译内容: 用于切割箱子或者喉咙的工具

文本内容: This is my BROOMSTICK! It can be used manually or braced with two hands to sweep items as you move. It has a telescopic handle for compact storage.
翻译内容: 这就是我的飞天扫帚！它可以被手动使用或者用两只手撑起，在你移动时清扫物品，他有个伸缩把手用于紧凑存储

文本内容: A vaguely humanoid cardboard cutout. It's completely blank.

文本内容: A cardboat cutout of an assistant.
A cardboard cutout of a clown. You get the feeling that it should be in a corner.

文本内容: A cardboard cutout of a traitor.

文本内容: A cardboard cutout of a servant of Ratvar.

文本内容: A cardboard cutout of a revolutionary.
A cardboard cutout of a wizard.
A cardboard cutout of a nightmare.
A cardboard cutout of a xenomorph.
A cardboard cutout of a xenomorph maid.

文本内容: A cardboard cutout of an ash walker.

文本内容: A cardboard cutout of a death commando.

文本内容: A cardboard cutout of the HoP's beloved corgi.
翻译内容: 一个HoP心爱的柯基的纸板模型

文本内容: A cardboard cutout of a slaughter demon.
翻译内容: 一个屠戮恶魔的纸板模型

文本内容: A cardboard cutout of a laughter demon.
翻译内容: 一个欢笑恶魔的纸板模型

文本内容: A cardboard cutout of a private security officer.
翻译内容: 一个私人安全官的纸板模型

文本内容: A card used to provide ID and determine access across the station.
翻译内容: 一个用于提供ID信息和在站点范围内的通行权限的卡

文本内容: A perfectly generic identification card. Looks like it could use some flavor.
翻译内容: 一张完美的普通ID卡，看来可以在上面定制一些东西

文本内容: A staff ID used to access the hotel's doors.
翻译内容: 一张工作人员的ID卡，用于进出旅馆的门

文本内容: A perfectly generic identification card. Looks like it could use some flavor.
翻译内容: 一张完美的普通ID卡，看来可以在上面定制一些东西

文本内容: Charlie Station Security Officer's ID card
A faded Charlie Station ID card. You can make out the rank \"Security Officer\".
翻译内容: 褪色的查理站ID卡，你能认出来职位是 \"安保警卫\"

文本内容: A faded Charlie Station ID card. You can make out the rank \"Scientist\".
翻译内容: 褪色的查理站ID卡，你能认出来职位是 \"科学家\"

文本内容: A faded Charlie Station ID card. You can make out the rank \"Station Engineer\".
翻译内容: 褪色的查理站ID卡，你能认出来职位是 \"站点工程师\"

文本内容: A special ID card that allows access to APC terminals.
翻译内容: 一张特别的ID卡，允许持有者访问APC终端
德尔塔站机器人学家的ID卡

文本内容: An ID card that allows access to bots maintenance protocols.
翻译内容: 一张ID卡，允许持有者使用机器人的维修协议

文本内容: Provides access to the departmental budget.
A card used to provide ID and determine access across the station. Has an integrated digital display and advanced microchips.
翻译内容: 一个用于提供ID信息和在站点范围内的通行权限的卡，拥有集成式数字显示器和高级微处理器

文本内容: A rainbow card, promoting fun in a 'business proper' sense!
翻译内容: 一张彩虹卡,在保持商业规范的同时促进乐趣!

文本内容: A silver card which shows honour and dedication.
翻译内容: 一张展现荣誉和贡献的银卡

文本内容: A golden card which shows power and might.
翻译内容: 一张展现权力和力量的金卡

文本内容: The spare ID of the High Lord himself.
翻译内容: 至高王本尊的备用 ID

文本内容: An ID straight from Central Command.
翻译内容: 来自中央指挥部的 ID
一张应急反应部队的ID卡

文本内容: This card is telling you one thing and one thing alone. The person holding this card is an utter badass.
翻译内容: 这张卡告诉你一件也只有一件事.就是拿着这张卡的人真牛逼.

文本内容: An ID straight from the Syndicate.
翻译内容: 一张来自于辛迪加的ID卡

文本内容: An ID straight from the Syndicate.
翻译内容: 一张来自于辛迪加的ID卡

文本内容: An ID straight from the Syndicate.
翻译内容: 一张来自于辛迪加的ID卡

文本内容: The spare ID of the Dark Lord himself.
A debug ID card. Has ALL the all access, you really shouldn't have this.
翻译内容: 一张Debug ID卡，拥有所有权限，你真的不应该拿到他

文本内容: You are a number, you are not a free man.
翻译内容: 现在的你不再是个自由人，而只是个编号。

文本内容: A highly advanced chameleon ID card. Touch this card on another ID card or player to choose which accesses to copy. Has special magnetic properties which force it to the front of wallets.
翻译内容: 一张高科技变色龙卡，使用磁卡触碰其他的ID卡或者玩家可以选择复制哪项访问权限，其拥有特别的磁吸设计，使其可以吸附在钱包的前面

文本内容: A card used to provide ID and determine access across the station. There's blood dripping from the corner. Ew.
翻译内容: 一个用于提供ID信息和在站点范围内的通行权限的卡.他的一角上还在滴着血.呕

文本内容: An internal ID card used by the station's non-sentient bots. You should report this to a coder if you're holding it.
翻译内容: 一种内置的ID卡，被站点的无意识机器人所使用，如果你能拿到他你应该向管理员汇报

文本内容: A card used to identify members of the red team for CTF
翻译内容: 用于识别 CTF 红队成员的ID卡

文本内容: A card used to identify members of the blue team for CTF
翻译内容: 用于识别 CTF 蓝队成员的ID卡

文本内容: A card used to identify members of the yellow team for CTF
翻译内容: 用于识别 CTF 黄队成员的ID卡

文本内容: A card used to identify members of the green team for CTF
翻译内容: 用于识别 CTF 绿队成员的ID卡

文本内容: A versatile power tool. Useful for limbing trees and delimbing humans.
翻译内容: 一种多功能电动工具。砍人和砍树的时候都很有用。

文本内容: A cunning device used to claim ownership of celestial bodies.
翻译内容: 一个用来认领天体所有权的狡猾装置。

文本内容: The banner bears the official coat of arms of Nanotrasen, signifying that [station_name()] has been claimed by Captain [uname] in the name of the company.
翻译内容: 旗帜上印有纳米传讯的官方盾徽，表示舰长[uname]已经以公司的名义获取了[station_name()]的所有权。

文本内容: A banner symbolizing a bloody victory over treacherous tyrants.
翻译内容: 象征着用血腥革命击败狡诈暴君的一面旗帜。

文本内容: A banner symbolizing a bloody victory over treacherous tyrants. The revolutionary leader [uname] has named the station [station_name()] to make clear that this station shall never be shackled by oppressors again.
翻译内容: 象征着用血腥革命击败狡诈暴君的一面旗帜。革命领袖[uname]将该站命名为[station_name()]，以明确表示该站永远不会再受压迫者所苦。

文本内容: Hey, why are you viewing this?!! Please let CentCom know about this odd occurrence.
翻译内容: 嘿，为啥你在看这玩意？！请快点让中央指挥部了解这件怪事。

文本内容: Summon a box of ingredients to help you get started cooking.
翻译内容: 召集一盒食材来开启你的烹饪之旅。

文本内容: To summon heroes from the past to protect the future.
翻译内容: 召唤旧日英雄来保护未来

文本内容: Summons augmentations. Can be used 3 times!
Contains a set of armaments for the chaplain.
翻译内容: 含有一套为牧师准备的装备.
用于保存染色体数据的管子

文本内容: A chromosome that reduces mutation instability by 20%.
翻译内容: 减少突变不稳定性20%的染色体。

文本内容: A chromosome that reduces mutation knockback and downsides by 50%.
翻译内容: 减轻突变50%不利影响的染色体

文本内容: A chromosome that increases mutation power by 50%.
翻译内容: 增强突变50%效果的染色体

文本内容: A chromosome that reduces action based mutation cooldowns by by 50%.
翻译内容: 加快突变充能50%的染色体

文本内容: A simple match stick, used for lighting fine smokables.
翻译内容: 一种简单的火柴，用来点燃精致的烟具。

文本内容: A [initial(name)]. This one has seen better days.
翻译内容: 一个 [initial(name)]，这一个已经见到好日子了

文本内容: An unlit firebrand. It makes you wonder why it's not just called a stick.
翻译内容: 一根未点燃的火柴，所以为什么不直接叫它一根棍子.

文本内容: A roll of tobacco and nicotine.
翻译内容: 用烟草和尼古丁卷成的纸卷。

文本内容: A Space brand cigarette that can be smoked anywhere.
翻译内容: 一包\"太空牌\"香烟——让你想在哪抽就在哪抽！

文本内容: A DromedaryCo brand cigarette. Contrary to popular belief, does not contain Calomel, but is reported to have a watery taste.
翻译内容: 一包\"单峰骆驼\"品牌香烟，与流行的观点相反，他并不含甘汞，但是有一股水味

文本内容: An Uplift Smooth brand cigarette. Smells refreshing.
翻译内容: 一包\"平滑上升\"牌香烟，气味清新
一包金版\"强健\"品牌香烟

文本内容: A Carp Classic brand cigarette. A small label on its side indicates that it does NOT contain carpotoxin.
翻译内容: 一包\"鲤鱼经典\"品牌香烟，有一个小标签在盒子的侧面表明了他不含任何鲤鱼毒

文本内容: A Shady Jim's Super Slims cigarette.
翻译内容: 一包\"阴暗吉姆\"的超细香烟
一包\"异形过滤器\"品牌香烟

文本内容: A roll of dried plant matter wrapped in thin paper.
翻译内容: 一卷包起来的干燥植物

文本内容: For all ages*! Doesn't contain any amount of nicotine. Health and safety risks can be read on the tip of the cigarette.
翻译内容: 全年龄*适用！不含任何尼古丁，可以从尖端读出健康和安全风险

文本内容: For all ages*! Doesn't contain any* amount of nicotine. Health and safety risks can be read on the tip of the cigarette.
翻译内容: 全年龄*适用！不含任何*尼古丁，可以从尖端读出健康和安全风险

文本内容: A manky old roach, or for non-stoners, a used rollup.
翻译内容: 一只老蟑螂，或者对于任何非石头人来说，用过的卷纸

文本内容: A brown roll of tobacco and... well, you're not quite sure. This thing's huge!
翻译内容: 一卷棕色的烟草……嗯，或许是吧。这东西也太大了！

文本内容: There's little more you could want from a cigar.
翻译内容: 这支雪茄已经好的不能再好了。

文本内容: A cigar fit for only the best of the best.
翻译内容: 只给精英中的精英准备的雪茄。

文本内容: A pipe, for smoking. Probably made of meerschaum or something.
翻译内容: 一根用来吸烟的烟斗。可能是用海泡石或者别的什么东西制成的。

文本内容: A nicotine delivery system popularized by folksy backwoodsmen and kept popular in the modern age and beyond by space hipsters. Can be loaded with objects.
翻译内容: 在民间的边远地区流行起来的一种一种尼古丁递送系统，并在现代及以后的太空潮人中都一直很流行。可以往里面装东西。

文本内容: A specialty zippo made from slimes and industry. Has a much hotter flame than normal.
翻译内容: 由史莱姆和工业制成的特制Zippo。 比普通款的火更热。

文本内容: A thin piece of paper used to make fine smokeables.
翻译内容: 用来制作精美可吸物品的薄纸 。

文本内容: A classy and highly sophisticated electronic cigarette, for classy and dignified gentlemen. A warning label reads \"Warning: Do not fill with flammable materials.\"
翻译内容: 一款优雅有格调的电子烟，为端庄优雅的绅士设计，上面有一块警告标志，写着\"警告: 不要填充可燃物.\"

文本内容: A cheap bar of soap. Doesn't smell.
翻译内容: 一块便宜香皂，没啥味道

文本内容: A homemade bar of soap. Smells of... well....
翻译内容: 一块自制肥皂，闻起来，呃哦

文本内容: A heavy duty bar of Nanotrasen brand soap. Smells of plasma.
翻译内容: 一大块纳米传讯品牌香皂，闻着像是等离子

文本内容: A deluxe Waffle Co. brand bar of soap. Smells of high-class luxury.
翻译内容: 一块豪华华夫公司牌的肥皂。高级豪华的味道。

文本内容: An untrustworthy bar of soap made of strong chemical agents that dissolve blood faster.
翻译内容: 一块不可靠的香皂，使用可以更快溶解血液的强大化学物质制成

文本内容: The most advanced soap known to mankind. The beginning of the end for germs.
翻译内容: 人类所知最先进的香皂。 这是细菌灭亡的开始。

文本内容: An old paper that has passed many hands.
翻译内容: 一张被人们传阅多次的旧纸。

文本内容: A horn off of a bicycle. Rumour has it that they're made from recycled clowns.
翻译内容: 从自行车上面摘下来的喇叭，有传言称他们是用回收小丑制造的

文本内容: Damn son, where'd you find this?
翻译内容: 臭小子，你在哪里找到这个的？

文本内容: Golden? Clearly, it's made with bananium! Honk!
翻译内容: 金子？很明显，他们是用香蕉矿做的！Honk！

文本内容: Just looking at this makes you want to giggle.
翻译内容: 光是看着这玩意你就想笑了

文本内容: This control wand can access any door on the station.
翻译内容: 这个遥控器可以遥控站点全部的门

文本内容: Remotely controls airlocks. This remote has additional Vault access.
翻译内容: 远程控制气闸，这个遥控器有额外的保险库许可
一根很常见品牌的口红

文本内容: An incredibly potent tube of lipstick made from the venom of the dreaded Yellow Spotted Space Lizard, as deadly as it is chic. Try not to smear it!
翻译内容: 这是一管极为强效的口红，由可怕的黄斑太空蜥蜴的毒液制成，既致命又时尚。尽量不要弄脏它！

文本内容: The latest and greatest power razor born from the science of shaving.
翻译内容: 最新的，也是最强大的电动剃须刀，由剃须科学制造

文本内容: Order, order! No bombs in my courthouse.
翻译内容: 秩序，保持秩序！我的法院里没有炸弹

文本内容: Smack it with a gavel hammer when the assistants get rowdy.
翻译内容: 当助手们开始为非作歹时，用你的木槌反复敲打

文本内容: This device raises pink levels to unknown highs.
翻译内容: 此设备将粉色级别提升到未知的最高点
纳米传讯 太空币市场

文本内容: This is good for spacecoin because
翻译内容: 这对太空币来讲很好，因为...

文本内容: A holographic projection designating the landing zone of something. It's probably best to stand back.
翻译内容: 指示某物着陆区域的全息投影，最好还是退后几步

文本内容: A colourful crayon. Looks tasty. Mmmm...
翻译内容: 彩色蜡笔。看起来很好吃。呣...
看起来非常悲伤的蜡笔

文本内容: A box of crayons for all your rune drawing needs.
翻译内容: 一盒蜡笔，满足你对符文绘制方面的所有需求。

文本内容: A metallic container containing tasty paint.
翻译内容: 一个装有美味油漆的金属容器。

文本内容: A metallic container containing shiny synthesised paint.
翻译内容: 一个装有闪亮合成漆的金属容器。

文本内容: This spraycan doesn't seem to be filled with paint...
翻译内容: 这个喷雾器似乎装的并不是油漆....

文本内容: You can barely keep hold of this thing.
翻译内容: 你几乎拿不住这个东西

文本内容: Art is best seen, not heard.
翻译内容: 艺术最好去看，而不是去听。
现在增加了30%的蓝空科技。

文本内容: A hard-light chip encoded with an amount of credits. It is a modern replacement for physical money that can be directly converted to virtual currency and viceversa. Keep away from magnets.
翻译内容: 用一定数量的信用点编译成的全息筹码，它是实物货币的现代替代品，可以直接转换为虚拟货币，反之亦然，远离磁铁

文本内容: Spawn a human by aiming at a turf and clicking. Use in hand to change type.
翻译内容: 瞄准一块地板点击刷出一个人类。在手中使用可切换类型。

文本内容: The original hypertool, born before them all. Use it in hand to unleash its true power.
翻译内容: 最初的超级工具，诞生于其他所有超级工具之前，使用它来释放它真正的力量。

文本内容: A belt-equipped defibrillator that can be rapidly deployed.
翻译内容: 可快速展开的腰带式除颤器。

文本内容: A belt-equipped blood-red defibrillator. Can revive through thick clothing, has an experimental self-recharging battery, and can be utilized in combat via applying the paddles in a disarming or aggressive manner.
翻译内容: 装配在腰带上的血红色除颤器。可以透过厚重衣物除颤伤者,装有一颗实验性的自充电电池,可以通过致残或杀伤方式用于作战情况

文本内容: A belt-equipped state-of-the-art defibrillator. Can revive through thick clothing, has an experimental self-recharging battery, and can be utilized in combat via applying the paddles in a disarming or aggressive manner.
翻译内容: 装配在腰带上的最先进除颤器.可以透过厚重衣物除颤伤者,装有一颗实验性的自充电电池,可以通过致残或杀伤方式用于作战情况.

文本内容: A pair of plastic-gripped paddles with flat metal surfaces that are used to deliver powerful electric shocks.
翻译内容: 一对带有金属平面的塑料抓握板，用于传递强大的电击。

文本内容: A pair of paddles used to revive deceased operatives. They possess both the ability to penetrate armor and to deliver powerful or disabling shocks offensively.
翻译内容: 一对用来救活死去特工的起搏器，他们不仅有穿透装甲的能力，还可以释放致命或者致残的电击
精英纳米传讯除颤电极板

文本内容: A pair of paddles used to revive deceased ERT members. They possess both the ability to penetrate armor and to deliver powerful or disabling shocks offensively.
翻译内容: 一对用来救活死去应急小队成员的起搏器，他们不仅有穿透装甲的能力，还可以释放致命或者致残的电击

文本内容: Contains all the luck you'll ever need.
翻译内容: 包含您所需的全部运气

文本内容: A die with six sides. Basic and serviceable.
A die with only one side. Deterministic!
翻译内容: 只有一面的骰子，可确定性！

文本内容: A die with two sides. Coins are undignified!
翻译内容: 一个两面骰。用硬币有失体面！

文本内容: A die with four sides. The nerd's caltrop.
翻译内容: 一个有四面的骰子，属于阿宅的菱角

文本内容: A die with six sides made of dense black wood. It feels cold and heavy in your hand.
翻译内容: 一个有六面的骰子，用高密度黑木制成，他感觉起来又重又凉

文本内容: A die with six sides. 6 TIMES 255 TIMES 255 TILE TOTAL EXISTENCE, SQUARE YOUR MIND OF EDUCATED STUPID: 2 DOES NOT EXIST.
翻译内容: 一个有六面的骰子，共有6面每面255格每格255个结果！让你的脑子清醒一点，傻瓜：2并不存在！

文本内容: A die with six sides but only three results. Is this a plus or a minus? Your mind is drawing a blank...
翻译内容: 一个拥有六个面但是只有三种结果的骰子，那是个加号还是减号？你的脑子一片空白

文本内容: A die with eight sides. It feels... lucky.
翻译内容: 有八面的骰子，感觉很幸运

文本内容: A die with ten sides. Useful for percentages.
翻译内容: 有十面的骰子，骰百分比很有用

文本内容: A die with ten sides. Works better for d100 rolls than a golf ball.
翻译内容: 有十面的骰子，在需要摇d100的时候比丢高尔夫球好使

文本内容: A die with twelve sides. There's an air of neglect about it.
翻译内容: 有十二面的骰子，感觉他被忽视了

文本内容: A die with twenty sides. The preferred die to throw at the GM.
翻译内容: 有二十面的骰子，往GM脸上投掷的首选骰子

文本内容: A die with one hundred sides! Probably not fairly weighted...
翻译内容: 一个有100面的骰子！虽然结果可能不是很公正

文本内容: A weird die with raised text printed on the faces. Everything's white on white so reading it is a struggle. What poor design!
翻译内容: 一个奇怪的骰子，文字是突印在上面的，通体白色，所以阅读这个是个灾难，什么烂设计！

文本内容: A die that exists in four dimensional space. Properly interpreting them can only be done with the help of a mathematician, a physicist, and a priest.
翻译内容: 一个存在于四维空间的骰子，只有在数学家、物理学家和牧师的帮助下才能正确解读

文本内容: A die with twenty sides. You can feel unearthly energies radiating from it. Using this might be VERY risky.
翻译内容: 一个有二十面的骰子，你可以感受到从它身上散发出的超凡脱俗的能量，使用它可能得冒巨大的风险

文本内容: A die with twenty sides. You feel that rolling this is a REALLY bad idea.
翻译内容: 一个有二十面的骰子，你真的觉得摇动他是个超级坏主意

文本内容: A die with twenty sides. The preferred die to throw at the GM.
翻译内容: 有二十面的骰子，往GM脸上投掷的首选骰子

文本内容: This spell can be used to call your servant, whenever you need it.
翻译内容: 这个咒语可以召唤你的仆人，当任何情况下你需要时

文本内容: A cheap single use autoinjector that injects the user with DNA.
翻译内容: 一种廉价的一次性自动注射器，可为用户注射DNA

文本内容: This will make you big and strong, but give you a bad skin condition.
翻译内容: 这个会让你又大又强壮，但对你的皮肤可能不太好

文本内容: Will make you a flea bag.
Activates the current mutation on injection, if the subject has it.
翻译内容: 如果对象拥有目标突变，则在注射时激活
将这个注射给安保小丑

文本内容: Will bring forth a sound of horror from your throat.
翻译内容: 会让你的喉咙发出糟糕的声音。
能够让你讨厌的咳嗽声停止

文本内容: Will make you hear once more.
It's a small world after all.
Helps you grow big and strong.

翻译内容: 不如此刻让我们尽情地一起摇摆~

文本内容: Will fix you up from shaking the room.
Will make you need dorkish glasses.
翻译内容: 会让你需要戴傻了吧唧的眼镜

文本内容: This will make you big and strong, but give you a bad skin condition.
翻译内容: 这个会让你又大又强壮，但对你的皮肤可能不太好

文本内容: Will make you a flea bag.

翻译内容: 能让你...不那么毛发旺盛
DNA注射器（反空间不稳定性）

文本内容: Good. Let the hate flow through you.
翻译内容: 很好，让仇恨流经你的全身

文本内容: Will make you not able to control your mind.
翻译内容: 让你没法继续用你的念力

文本内容: Gives you a nasty case of Tourette's.
翻译内容: 让你得上讨厌的污言秽语综合征
能治好你的污言秽语综合征

文本内容: Finally you can see what the Captain does.
翻译内容: 终于你能看到舰长到底在干啥了

文本内容: It will make you see harder.
Can be used to take chemical and genetic samples of pretty much anything.
翻译内容: 可以采集来自几乎任何东西的化学和基因样本。

文本内容: Can be used to take chemical and genetic samples of animals.
翻译内容: 可以采集来自动物的化学和基因样本

文本内容: A brace used to seal and reinforce an airlock. Useful for making areas inaccessible to those without opposable thumbs.
翻译内容: 一个用于密封和加固气闸的支架。可以让那些没有对生拇指的人进不去。

文本内容: A congealed glob of pure saturnX.\nThis compound was first discovered during the infancy of cloaking technology and at the time thought to be a promising candidate agent. It was withdrawn for consideration after the researchers discovered a slew of associated safety issues including thought disorders and hepatoxicity.\nIt has since attained some limited popularity as a street drug.
翻译内容: 纯真的土星X凝结球体\n这种化合物最初是在隐身技术的初期发现的，当时被认为是一种很有前途的候选制剂。研究人员发现了包括思维障碍和肝毒性在内的一系列相关安全问题后，该研究被撤回考虑\n作为街头毒品，它的受欢迎程度有限

文本内容: A small hard lump of kronkaine freebase.\nIt is said the average kronkaine addict causes as much criminal damage as four cat burglars, two arsonists and one rabid pit bull terrier combined.
翻译内容: 一小块硬化的精炼\"克朗凯恩\"\n据说，平均每个克朗凯恩毒瘾者所造成的刑事损失相当于四名猫贼、两名纵火犯和一只狂犬病斗牛犬的总和

文本内容: A small ampoule. The liquid inside appears to be boiling violently.\nYou suspect it contains bLasSToFF; the drug thought to be the cause of the infamous Luna nightclub mass casualty incident.
翻译内容: 一个小安瓿，里面的液体似乎沸腾得很厉害\n您怀疑它包含癫火起飞；这种药物被认为是臭名昭著的Luna夜总会大规模伤亡事件的原因

文本内容: A double bladed energy sword employed by the Syndicate in raids
翻译内容: 一把辛迪加组织在袭击中使用的双刃能量剑

文本内容: A spray to dye hair as well as giving it any gradient you'd like.
翻译内容: 一种喷剂，可以把头发染成你想要的任何颜色，包括渐变色

文本内容: A black ball with a stenciled number eight in white on the side. It seems full of dark liquid.\nThe instructions state that you should ask your question aloud, and then shake.
翻译内容: 一个侧面印有白色数字8的黑球。它似乎充满了黑色液体\n说明书上说你应该大声问问题，然后摇晃

文本内容: A black ball with a stenciled number eight in white on the side. It is cracked and seems empty.
翻译内容: 一个侧面印有白色数字8的黑球，它裂开了，里面的液体似乎已经流光了

文本内容: It's a card with a magnetic strip attached to some circuitry.
翻译内容: 它是一张带有磁条的卡，连接到一些电路装置上

文本内容: An specially modified ID card used to break machinery and disable safeties. Notoriously used by Syndicate agents.
翻译内容: 一种经过特殊修改的ID卡，用于破坏机器和禁用安全装置。被臭名昭著的辛迪加特工们所使用。

文本内容: It's a blue card with a magnetic strip attached to some circuitry. It appears to have some sort of transmitter attached to it.
翻译内容: 这是一张蓝色的卡片，上面有一条磁条连接在一些电路上，它似乎连接了某种发射器

文本内容: It's a pumpkin with a cryptographic sequencer sticking out.
翻译内容: 这是一个南瓜，有一张密码测序器从中突出

文本内容: It's a card with a magnetic strip attached to some circuitry.
翻译内容: 它是一张带有磁条的卡，连接到一些电路装置上

文本内容: Closer inspection shows that this card is a poorly made replica, with a \"DonkCo\" logo stamped on the back.
翻译内容: 仔细检查表明，这张卡片是一张制作拙劣的复制品，背面印有\"DonkCo\"的标志

文本内容: This dated-looking ID card has been obviously and illegally modified with extra circuitry. Resembles the infamous \"emag\".
翻译内容: 这张看起来过时的ID卡显然已经被非法改装了额外的电路，类似于臭名昭著的\"emag\"

文本内容: Identifies commonly as a \"doorjack\", this illegally modified ID card can disrupt airlock electronics. Has a self recharging cell. Used often by Syndicate agents.
翻译内容: 这张非法修改过的ID卡可以破坏气闸里的电子元件，通常被认为是\"顶门器\"。内置自充电电池。被臭名昭著的辛迪加特工所使用。
战列巡洋舰坐标上传卡
便携式以太迪斯科灯球

文本内容: Press the button for a deployment of slightly-unethical PARTY!
翻译内容: 按下这个按钮来开始一场稍微有点不道德的派对！

文本内容: The ethics of this discoball are questionable.
翻译内容: 这场迪斯科舞会的道德规范值得怀疑。
一个传统的红色灭火器。

文本内容: A light and compact fibreglass-framed model fire extinguisher.
翻译内容: 一个轻型的玻璃纤维灭火器

文本内容: Spraycan turned coolant dipsenser. Can be sprayed on containers to cool them. Refll using water.
翻译内容: 一个能喷出冷却液的喷漆罐，可以喷在容器上来冷却他们，需要用水来重装

文本内容: Used to stop thermonuclear fires from spreading inside your engine.
翻译内容: 用于遏制热核火灾在你的引擎中蔓延

文本内容: Truly, the weapon of a madman. Who would think to fight fire with an axe?
翻译内容: 确实，疯子的武器，你怎么用斧头来灭火？

文本内容: A large, vicious axe crafted out of several sharpened bone plates and crudely tied together. Made of monsters, by killing monsters, for killing monsters.
翻译内容: 一把大斧，用几块锋利的骨板制成，粗暴地绑在一起，材质来源于怪，原料由杀戮而来，用于更多无尽杀戮

文本内容: A lightweight crowbar with an extreme sharp fire axe head attached. It trades it's hefty as a weapon by making it easier to carry around when holstered to suits without having to sacrifice your backpack.
翻译内容: 一个带有超级锐利斧头的轻型撬棍，它的在作为武器时的优势是，由于更轻，可以轻松将其携带在你的皮带上，而不需要牺牲你宝贵的背包空间

文本内容: plastic box containing gun maintenance supplies and spare parts. Use them on a Mosin Nagant to clean it.
翻译内容: 塑料盒装的枪械维护用品和备用件，在莫辛纳甘上面使用它来清洁

文本内容: Use this to keep prisoners in line.
Fake handcuffs meant for gag purposes.
翻译内容: 用于做一些奇怪事情的假手铐

文本内容: Looks like some cables tied together. Could be used to tie something up.
翻译内容: 看上去像是一些线缆困在一起，可以用来捆绑什么东西

文本内容: A pair of restraints fashioned from long strands of flesh.
翻译内容: 一对由长长的肉丝制成的束带

文本内容: Plastic, disposable zipties that can be used to restrain temporarily but are destroyed after use.
翻译内容: 一次性扎带，可用于暂时性约束，使用后会被破坏

文本内容: Fake zipties meant for gag purposes.
翻译内容: 用于做一些奇怪事情的假扎带

文本内容: A pair of broken fake zipties.
Use this to keep prisoners in line.
A trap used to catch bears and other legged creatures.
翻译内容: 用来捕捉熊和其他有腿生物的陷阱

文本内容: A restraining device designed to be thrown at the target. Upon connecting with said target, it will wrap around their legs, making it difficult for them to move quickly.
翻译内容: 一种设计用于向目标投掷的约束装置，接触到目标后，会缠绕在他们的腿上，让他们难以移动

文本内容: A strong bola, made with a long steel chain. It looks heavy, enough so that it could trip somebody.
翻译内容: 一个强大的抛绳，用长长的铁链做成，他看起来很沉，以至于能绊倒别人

文本内容: A specialized hard-light bola designed to ensnare fleeing criminals and aid in arrests.
翻译内容: 一种专门用于追捕逃跑罪犯和协助逮捕的硬光抛绳

文本内容: Hey, if you have to be hugged in the legs by anything, it might as well be this little guy.
翻译内容: 如果非要被什么东西抱在腿上，那是这个小家伙好了

文本内容: If somebody looks at this while it's below your waist, you get to bop them.
翻译内容: 如果你把手放在腰以下时候有人看，你就可以弹他们

文本内容: Get someone in an aggressive grab then use this on them to ruin their day.
翻译内容: 抓住别人然后用它来毁掉他们的好心情

文本内容: This is how real men fight.
Your filthy little fingers are ready to commit crimes.
翻译内容: 你肮脏的小手指头已经准备好犯罪了。

文本内容: I want you all to know, everyone and anyone, to seal it with a kiss.
翻译内容: 我想让你们所有人知道，以吻封缄。

文本内容: If looks could kill, they'd be this.
翻译内容: 如果美丽也能杀人，那就会像是这样。

文本内容: french kiss (is that a hint of garlic?)
翻译内容: 法式湿吻（那是大蒜味吗？）

文本内容: A toolbox painted bright green. Looking at it makes you feel uneasy.
翻译内容: 一个漆成亮绿色的工具箱。看着它会让你感到不安。

文本内容: A bloodthirsty artifact created by a profane rite.
翻译内容: 由一个亵渎的仪式所制造出的嗜血制品。

文本内容: A legendary toolbox and a distant artifact from The Age of Three Powers. On its three latches engraved are the words \"The Sun\", \"The Moon\", and \"The Stars\". The entire toolbox has the words \"The World\" engraved into its sides.
翻译内容: 一个传说中的工具箱和来自三力时代的一件遥远的手工艺品。它的三个门闩上刻着 \"太阳\"、\"月亮\"和\"星星\"。整个工具箱的侧面刻有 \"世界\"字样。

文本内容: A handy-dandy holographic projector that displays a janitorial sign.
翻译内容: 一个方便的、漂亮的全息投影仪，可以显示一个清洁标志。

文本内容: A holographic projector that creates hard light wet floor barriers.
翻译内容: 一个制造全息小心地滑警示牌的全息投影仪。
安全部门全息屏障投影仪

文本内容: A holographic projector that creates holographic security barriers.
翻译内容: 一个制造全息安全屏障的全息投影仪。
工程部门全息屏障投影仪

文本内容: A holographic projector that creates holographic engineering barriers.
翻译内容: 一个制造全息工程屏障的全息投影仪。

文本内容: A holographic projector that creates holographic barriers that prevent changes in atmosphere conditions.
翻译内容: 一种全息投影仪，它能产生全息屏障，防止大气状态的变化

文本内容: A holographic projector that creates PENLITE holobarriers. Useful during quarantines since they halt those with malicious diseases.
翻译内容: 一个制造PENLITE屏障的全息投影仪，有阻挡住患有不良疾病者的能力因此适用于制造隔离区

文本内容: A holographic projector that creates fragile energy fields.
翻译内容: 一个创造脆弱能量场的全息投影仪。

文本内容: A rod of pure obsidian; its very presence disrupts and dampens 'magical forces'. That's what the guidebook says, anyway.
翻译内容: 这是一根由纯黑曜石制成的棍子，这个特殊的存在破坏了大部分的魔法力量，至少说明书上是这么说的

文本内容: This hand of yours glows with an awesome power!
翻译内容: 你的手散发着令人敬畏的力量！

文本内容: It has a mysterious, protective aura.
翻译内容: 它形成了一种神秘的保护立场

文本内容: A weapon fit for a crusade!
翻译内容: 适合十字军东征的武器！

文本内容: Spread the glory of the dark gods!
Suffer not a heretic to live.
翻译内容: 记住，不要让任何一个异端活着

文本内容: The blade glows with the power of faith. Or possibly a battery.
翻译内容: 这把刀闪烁着信仰的力量，也可能只是电池

文本内容: Capable of cutting clean through a holy claymore.
翻译内容: 能够轻松斩断一把神圣阔剑。

文本内容: Once the harbinger of an interdimensional war, its sharpness fluctuates wildly.
翻译内容: 作为一场跨维度战争的先兆，它的尖锐程度波动很大

文本内容: If you strike me down, I shall become more robust than you can possibly imagine.
翻译内容: 如果你把我打倒，我会变得比你想象的更强健

文本内容: Woefully ineffective when used on steep terrain.
翻译内容: 在陡峭的地形上使用时，效果不佳

文本内容: Convincing HR that your religion involved piracy was no mean feat.
翻译内容: 让人事部相信你的宗教信仰涉及海盗事业决不是有意的

文本内容: This thing is so unspeakably HOLY you are having a hard time even holding it.
翻译内容: 这东西真是难以形容，我的上帝，你就连拿着它都像是经历了一段痛苦的时光

文本内容: Ask not for whom the bell tolls...
Bad references are the DNA of the soul.
The blade grants the wielder nearly limitless power...if they can figure out how to turn it on, that is.
翻译内容: 一把能够赋予使用者无穷力量的刀刃…前提是他们能找到打开的办法

文本内容: When the station falls into chaos, it's nice to have a friend by your side.
翻译内容: 当太空站陷入混乱时，还有个朋友在你身边再好不过了。

文本内容: Suffer not a heretic to live.
翻译内容: 记住，不要让任何一个异端活着。

文本内容: This war hammer cost the chaplain forty thousand space dollars.
翻译内容: 这把战锤花了牧师四万太空币。

文本内容: Good? Bad? You're the guy with the chainsaw hand.
翻译内容: 是好事，还是坏事？不管如何，你是个装着链锯手的家伙。

文本内容: It resonates an aura of Pride.
翻译内容: 它能产生一个骄傲光环。

文本内容: What a terrible night to be on Space Station 13.
翻译内容: 十三号太空站上的人们度过了多么糟糕的夜晚。

文本内容: The brim of the hat is as sharp as your wit. The edge would hurt almost as much as disproving the existence of God.
翻译内容: 帽檐如你的智慧一般锋芒毕露，它的也拥有和证伪神明相匹配的威力。

文本内容: Particularly twisted deities grant gifts of dubious value.
翻译内容: 极度扭曲的众神赐予的可疑礼物

文本内容: An adorable stuffed toy that resembles the god of all carp. The teeth look pretty sharp. Activate it to receive the blessing of Carp-Sie.
翻译内容: 一个好似太空鱼之神的可爱毛绒玩具，它的牙齿看上去很锋利，激活它可以接受太空鱼神的祝福。

文本内容: A long, tall staff made of polished wood. Traditionally used in ancient old-Earth martial arts, it is now used to harass the clown.
翻译内容: 一个用抛光木制成的又长又高的杖。过去曾在古代旧地球的武术中使用，现在被用来暴揍那些蠢货。

文本内容: They say fear is the true mind killer, but stabbing them in the head works too. Honour compels you to not sheathe it once drawn.
翻译内容: 他们说恐惧才是意志的克星，但是刺他们的头一样有用，一旦出鞘，利刃的荣耀不允许你再次收回。

文本内容: Holding this makes you look absolutely devilish.
翻译内容: 拿着这个绝对会让你看起来像个恶魔。

文本内容: A tutorial in mummification is carved into the staff. You could probably craft the wraps if you had some cloth.
翻译内容: 在手杖上雕刻有木乃伊的制作教程，如果你有布料可以自己试试包一个。

文本内容: A tool so powerful even you cannot perfectly use it.
翻译内容: 一个强大到连你都无法完美使用的工具。

文本内容: An ancient spear made of brass, I mean gold, I mean bronze. It looks highly mechanical.
翻译内容: 一支由黄铜制成的远古长矛，我是指它是由黄金和青铜做的，看起来十分精巧。

文本内容: A label on the side of this potato reads \"Product of Donk Co. Service Wing. Activate far away from populated areas. Device will only attach to sapient creatures.\" You can attack anyone with it to force it on them instead of yourself!
A label on the side of this potato reads \"Product of Donk Co. Toys and Recreation department.\" You can attack anyone with it to put it on them instead, if they have a free hand to take it!
Nanotrasen patented gravity invariant hourglass. Guaranteed to flow perfectly under any conditions.
翻译内容: 纳米传讯专利恒定重力沙漏，保证任何环境下都能完美流动

文本内容: A tool for inductively charging internal power cells.
翻译内容: 一个用于给内部电池无线充电的工具

文本内容: A tool for inductively charging internal power cells. This one has a science color scheme, and is less potent than its engineering counterpart.
翻译内容: 一个用于给内部电池无线充电的工具，有着科研部配色，充电效率低于工程版本

文本内容: A tool for inductively charging internal power cells. This one has a suspicious colour scheme, and seems to be rigged to transfer charge at a much faster rate.
翻译内容: 一个用于给内部电池无线充电的工具，有着可疑的配色，似乎被改装过以提高充电效率

文本内容: Central Command-issued inspection device. Performs inspections according to Nanotrasen protocols when activated, then prints an encrypted report regarding the maintenance of the station. Definitely not giving you cancer.
翻译内容: 中央指挥部下发的视察仪，激活时会根据纳米传讯协议开始检查，然后打印出一份有关空间站维护的加密报告，绝不会让你得癌症

文本内容: Contains no information about the station's current status.
翻译内容: 不包含任何关于空间站当前状态的信息

文本内容: Contains detailed information about the station's current status.
翻译内容: 包含有关于空间站当前状态的详细信息
香蕉石洪克型光子扫描仪

文本内容: Contains no information about the station's current status.
翻译内容: 不包含任何关于空间站当前状态的信息

文本内容: A little bit of nature contained in a pot.
翻译内容: 在花盆里装着一点自然的气息。

文本内容: A gift from the botanical staff, presented after the RD's reassignment. There's a tag on it that says \"Y'all come back now, y'hear?\"\nIt doesn't look very healthy...
翻译内容: 在研究部长人事分配后来自植物学家部门的礼物。上面的标签写着“你们都回来了？” 这看起来不是非常健康...

文本内容: Something that seems to have been made by the Nanotrasen science division, one might call it an abomination. It's heads seem... alive.
翻译内容: 似乎是纳米传讯研发部制造的，一些人会将其称为怪物，它的头看起来是…活的

文本内容: A fake, cheap looking, plastic tree. Perfect for people who kill every plant they touch.
翻译内容: 一棵假的，看起来就相当廉价的塑料树，非常适合那些会杀死他们碰过的每一颗植物的人。

文本内容: A secret agent staffed in the station's bar to protect the mystical cakehat.
翻译内容: 一名为保护神秘蛋糕帽而被安插在空间站酒吧的秘密特工。

文本内容: An old botanical research sample collected on a long forgotten jungle planet.
翻译内容: 在一个被遗忘已久的丛林星球收集的一个古老的植物学研究样本。

文本内容: Really takes you back to highschool lunch.
翻译内容: 确实能让你回想起高中的午饭。

文本内容: A general purpose Chef's Knife made by SpaceCook Incorporated. Guaranteed to stay sharp for years to come.
翻译内容: 由太空烹饪公司生产的通用厨师刀，保证未来几年都能锋利。

文本内容: A very safe, barely sharp knife made of plastic. Good for cutting food and not much else.
翻译内容: 一个超级安全，用塑料制成的完全不锋利的刀。适合用来切食物，除此之外没啥用。

文本内容: Used to knock out the Bartender.
Just be careful your food doesn't melt the spoon first.
翻译内容: 注意，可别让你的食物把勺子先给融了。

文本内容: The original knife, it is said that all other knives are only copies of this one.
翻译内容: 原型刀，据说所有其他的刀都只是这把的复制品。

文本内容: The unearthly energies that once powered this blade are now dormant.
翻译内容: 曾经驱动这把刀刃的神秘力量现在沉寂了下来。

文本内容: An occult looking dagger that is cold to the touch. Somehow, the flawless orb on the pommel is made entirely of liquid blood.
翻译内容: 一把冰冷的神秘匕首，出于某种原因，剑柄上完美无瑕的球体完全由流动的血液制成。

文本内容: A huge thing used for chopping and chopping up meat. This includes clowns and clown by-products.
翻译内容: 用来剁肉的大家伙。这包括小丑和类小丑。

文本内容: Despite its name, it's mainly used for cutting meat from dead prey rather than actual hunting.
翻译内容: 尽管它叫猎刀，但它主要用于从死去的猎物上切下肉，而不是真正的用来狩猎。

文本内容: A military combat utility survival knife.
翻译内容: 一个无论战斗还是求生都很实用的军用刀。
一个狩猎级的生存用刀。

文本内容: A sharpened bone. The bare minimum in survival.
翻译内容: 尖锐的骨头，生存的最低限度。

文本内容: A cyborg-mounted plasteel knife. Extremely sharp and durable.
翻译内容: 一把安装在赛博格上的钢刀，极其锋利耐用。
一把临时的等离子玻璃小刀
一把临时的钛钢玻璃小刀

文本内容: A makeshift titanium-infused plasma glass shiv.
翻译内容: 一把临时的等离子钛钢玻璃小刀，好吧，我想他不再是临时武器了

文本内容: Unlike other carrots, you should probably keep this far away from your eyes.
翻译内容: 和其他胡萝卜不一样的是，你最好把它放得离你的眼睛远一点。

文本内容: An officially postmarked, tamper-evident parcel regulated by CentCom and made of high-quality materials.
翻译内容: 由中央管制的，加盖中央指挥部防揭邮戳的包裹，由优质材料制成。

文本内容: A certified post crate from CentCom.
翻译内容: 一个由中央司令部认证的邮件箱。

文本内容: A certified post crate from CentCom. Looks stuffed to the gills.
翻译内容: 一个由中央司令部认证的邮件箱，看起来被完全填满了。

文本内容: A bag for letters, envelopes, and other postage.
翻译内容: 装信件、信封和其他邮资的袋子。

文本内容: A type of primitive battery. It is quite large feels unexpectedly heavy.
翻译内容: 一种古老的电池，它相当大，并且出乎意料地沉重

文本内容: The Human Harvest: From Seed to Market
翻译内容: 人类的丰收：从种子到出售
APLU \"Ripley\" 建造和操作使用手册

文本内容: Corporate Regulations" //SKYRAT EDIT CHANGE - Original: "Space Law

A set of Nanotrasen regulations for keeping law, order, and procedure followed within their space stations." //SKYRAT EDIT CHANGE - Original: "A set of Nanotrasen guidelines for keeping law and order on their space stations.

翻译内容: 流行病学——制造你自己的流行病!
传送科学——蓝空的仿制品！

文本内容: The Film Noir: Proper Procedures for Investigations
翻译内容: 玄色影戏：适当的调查程序

文本内容: Barman Recipes: Mixing Drinks and Changing Lives
Ordnance for Dummies or: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Maxcap
翻译内容: 傻瓜军械学 或者：我如何学会不再担忧并且爱上Maxcap

文本内容: The world of janitalia wouldn't be complete without a mop.
翻译内容: 没有拖把的世界对于清洁工来说不完美。

文本内容: The most advanced tool in a custodian's arsenal, complete with a condenser for self-wetting! Just think of all the viscera you will clean up with this! Due to the self-wetting technology, it proves very inefficient for cleaning up spills.
翻译内容: 在看门人的武器库里最先进的工具，完全由冷凝器自我润湿!想想用这个你能清理的多少内脏啊!由于自我润湿技术，它被证明是非常低效的清理溅出液体的工具。

文本内容: A weird brown crystal, it smokes when broken
翻译内容: 怪异的棕色晶体，在破碎时会释放烟雾

文本内容: Used to recolor floors and walls. Can be removed by the janitor.
翻译内容: 用来给地板和墙壁重新上色，可由清洁工移除。

文本内容: Used to remove color from anything.
翻译内容: 用来去除任何东西的颜色。

文本内容: A flexible coated cable with a universal jack on one end.
翻译内容: 一端有万向插孔的柔性涂层电缆。

文本内容: A big white-and-blue pet carrier. Good for carrying <s>meat to the chef</s> cute animals around.
翻译内容: 一个巨大的蓝白相间的宠物背包，适合携带<s>肉给厨师</s>可爱的动物。

文本内容: Alien device used for undescribable purpose. Or carrying pets.
翻译内容: 用于无法描述目的的外星设备，或许可以拿来携带宠物。

文本内容: A handheld tracking device that locks onto certain signals.
翻译内容: 锁定特定信号的手持式跟踪设备。

文本内容: A handheld tracking device that points to crew suit sensors.
翻译内容: 指向船员连身衣传感器信号的手持式跟踪设备。

文本内容: A handheld tracking device that locks onto its other half of the matching pair.
翻译内容: 一种手持追踪装置，锁定配对的另一半。

文本内容: A handheld tracking device that locates the bounty hunter shuttle for quick escapes.
翻译内容: 一个手持式追踪装置，可以定位赏金猎人的飞船，以便快速逃离。

文本内容: A simple tool used for moving hay.
This is the special coder plush, do not steal.
翻译内容: 这是编码机专用的毛绒，不要偷窃。

文本内容: [src] is a little baby of [maternal_parent] and [paternal_parent]!
An adorable stuffed toy that resembles a space carp.
翻译内容: 一个可爱的毛绒玩具，看起来像一条太空鲤鱼。

文本内容: The friendly red demon that gives good miners gifts.
翻译内容: 一个友好的红色恶魔，送给优秀矿工的礼物。

文本内容: An adorable plushie of the clockwork justiciar himself with new and improved spring arm action.
翻译内容: 一个可爱的毛绒发条法官正在使用自己崭新并且改进过的弹簧手臂行动。

文本内容: A small stuffed doll of the elder goddess Nar'Sie. Who thought this was a good children's toy?
翻译内容: 上古女神纳尔西的小毛绒娃娃，是谁认为这适合做成儿童玩具的?

文本内容: An adorable stuffed toy that resembles a lizardperson.
翻译内容: 一个像蜥蜴人的可爱毛绒玩具。

文本内容: An adorable stuffed toy that resembles a green lizardperson. This one fills you with nostalgia and soul.
翻译内容: 一个可爱的毛绒玩具，像一个绿色的蜥蜴人。这让你充满了怀旧之情和来自灵魂的气魄。

文本内容: An adorable stuffed toy that resembles a very determined spacefaring lizardperson. To infinity and beyond, little guy.
翻译内容: 一个可爱的毛绒玩具，看起来像一个非常坚定的太空蜥蜴人，飞向比无限更遥远的地方吧，小家伙。

文本内容: An adorable stuffed toy that resembles a snake. Not to be mistaken for the real thing.
翻译内容: 一个像蛇的可爱毛绒玩具，可别认成真蛇了。

文本内容: A stuffed toy that resembles a syndicate nuclear operative. The tag claims operatives to be purely fictitious.
翻译内容: 一个长得像辛迪加核特工的毛绒玩具，标签声称这些特工完全是虚构的。

文本内容: A stuffed toy that resembles your purple coworkers. Mmm, yeah, in true plasmaman fashion, it's not cute at all despite the designer's best efforts.
翻译内容: 一个像你紫色同事的毛绒玩具，嗯，是的，在真正的等离子人的领域中，它一点都不可爱，尽管设计师尽了最大的努力。

文本内容: An adorable stuffed toy that resembles a slime. It is practically just a hacky sack.
翻译内容: 一种像史莱姆一样可爱的填充玩具，它实际上就是一个干涩的大麻袋。

文本内容: An ancient plushie that has grown enlightened to the true nature of reality.
翻译内容: 一个逐渐理解了现实本质的远古玩偶。

文本内容: A cute toy that resembles an even cuter bee.
翻译内容: 一个可爱的玩具，像一只更可爱的蜜蜂。

文本内容: Despite its cuddly appearance and plush nature, it will beat you up all the same. Goats never change.
翻译内容: 尽管它有令人喜爱的外观和毛绒的质感，但它仍然会揍你，山羊就是那么顽固。

文本内容: A plushie depicting an adorable mothperson. It's a huggable bug!
翻译内容: 一个看起来非常可爱的蛾人毛绒玩具，这是一个可爱到令人想拥抱的小家伙!

文本内容: A plushie depicting an unsettling mothperson. After killing [suicide_count] [suicide_count == 1 ? "person" : "people"] it's not looking so huggable now...
翻译内容: 一个看起来令人毛骨悚然的毛绒蛾人玩具. 在它杀了[suicide_count] [suicide_count == 1 ? "个人" : "个人"]之后显得不再那么亲和了...

文本内容: A plushie depicting a creepy mothperson. It's killed [suicide_count] people! I don't think I want to hug it any more!
翻译内容: 一个看起来令人毛骨悚然的毛绒蛾人玩具. 它杀死了[suicide_count]个人！我不想再抱它了！

文本内容: A plushie depicting a peacekeeper cyborg. Only you can prevent human harm!
翻译内容: 一件毛绒玩具，描绘了一个维和者赛博格的形象，只有你才能保护人类安全!

文本内容: A plushie depicting a xenomorph runner, made to commemorate the centenary of the Battle of LV-426. Much cuddlier than the real thing.
翻译内容: 为纪念LV-426战役一百周年而制作的一件描绘一个异型信使的毛绒玩具，比真的要可爱多了。

文本内容: A plushie depicting an alien abductor. The tag on it is in an indecipherable language.
翻译内容: 外星人绑架者形象的毛绒玩具，上面的标签是一种无法辨认的语言。

文本内容: A plushie depicting an alien abductor agent. The stun baton is attached to the hand of the plushie, and appears to be inert. I wouldn't stay alone with it.
翻译内容: 一个描绘外星人绑架特工的毛绒玩具，一根电棍绑在毛绒玩偶的手上，看起来没有启动，我可不想独自和它共处一室。

文本内容: A plushie depicting a large cucumber with eyes, it seems that according to the manufacturer of the toy, the human race will look like in the future.
翻译内容: 这个毛绒玩具描绘了一个长着眼睛的大黄瓜，根据玩具的制造商的说法，人类在未来的样子似乎是这样的。

文本内容: A gas-powered cannon that can fire any object loaded into it.
翻译内容: 一门以气体为动力的大炮，可以发射任何装进去的物体。

文本内容: A gas-powered, object-firing cannon made out of common parts.
翻译内容: 一种由通用零件制成的以气体为动力的物体发射器。

文本内容: Load cream pie for optimal results.
翻译内容: 装入奶油馅饼以获得最佳效果。

文本内容: A metal gauntlet with a piston-powered ram ontop for that extra 'ompfh' in your punch.
翻译内容: 一个金属护手，上面有一个活塞驱动的动力锤，可以让你的出拳更有\"冲击力\"。

文本内容: This feels like it belongs to a door.
翻译内容: 这感觉就像属于一扇门。

文本内容: A yellow keycard. How fantastic. Looks like it belongs to a high security door.
翻译内容: 一张黄色的钥匙卡。真是太棒了。看起来它属于一扇高度安全的门。

文本内容: A blue keycard. How terrific. Looks like it belongs to a high security door.
翻译内容: 一张蓝色的钥匙卡。真是太棒了。看起来它属于一扇高度安全的门。

文本内容: This door only opens under certain conditions. It looks virtually indestructible.
翻译内容: 此门仅在特定条件下打开。它看起来几乎坚不可摧。

文本内容: This door only opens when a keycard is swiped. It looks virtually indestructible.
翻译内容: 这扇门只在刷卡时打开。它看起来几乎坚不可摧。

文本内容: It looks like it requires a yellow keycard.
翻译内容: 看起来它需要一张黄色的钥匙卡。

文本内容: It looks like it requires a blue keycard.
翻译内容: 看起来它需要一张蓝色的钥匙卡。

文本内容: This door only opens when a linked mechanism is powered. It looks virtually indestructible.
翻译内容: 此门仅在与其相联接的机械装置通电时打开。它看起来几乎坚不可摧。

文本内容: A hard-light box, containing a secure decryption key.
翻译内容: 一个用于装安全秘钥的硬光箱。

文本内容: A high power, electronic input port for a holobox, which can unlock the hologrid's storage compartment. Safe to stand on.
翻译内容: 全息箱的高功率电子输入端口，可以打开全息箱，站在上面并不会电到你

文本内容: It's a mechanism that seems to power something when all the lights are lit up. It looks virtually indestructible.
翻译内容: 当所有的灯都亮起来的时候，这是一种给什么东西供电的机械，它看起来几乎坚不可摧。

文本内容: A device used to rapidly build and deconstruct. Reload with iron, plasteel, glass or compressed matter cartridges.
翻译内容: 一种用于快速建造和分解的装置，用铁，钢板，玻璃或压缩物质筒装弹。
快捷建设装置：切换至玻璃窗
快捷建设装置：切换窗户大小

文本内容: A device used to rapidly build walls and floors.
翻译内容: 用于快速建造墙壁和地板的设备。

文本内容: Highly compressed matter for the RCD.
翻译内容: 用于快捷建设装置的高度压缩物质。

文本内容: A prototype RCD with ranged capability and extended capacity. Reload with iron, plasteel, glass or compressed matter cartridges.
翻译内容: 这是具有远程能力和扩展能力的RCD原型，用铁，钢板，玻璃或压缩物质筒装弹。

文本内容: A device used to rapidly provide lighting sources to an area. Reload with iron, plasteel, glass or compressed matter cartridges.
翻译内容: 一种快速为某一区域提供光源的装置，用铁，钢板，玻璃或压缩物质筒装弹。

文本内容: A device used to rapidly provide lighting sources to an area. Reload with iron, plasteel, glass or compressed matter cartridges.
翻译内容: 一种快速为某一区域提供光源的装置，用铁，钢板，玻璃或压缩物质筒装弹。

文本内容: An expertly modified RCD outfitted to construct plumbing machinery.
翻译内容: 一种经过专业改装的快捷建设装置，用于建造管道机械。

文本内容: A type of plumbing constructor designed to rapidly deploy the machines needed to conduct cytological research.
翻译内容: 一种用于快速部署细胞学研究所需机器的管道构建器。

文本内容: A type of plumbing constructor designed to rapidly deploy the machines needed to make a brewery.
翻译内容: 一种管道构造器，用于快速部署啤酒厂所需的机器。
快捷建设装置高级设计磁盘

文本内容: It contains the design for machine frames and computer frames.
翻译内容: 它包含机器框架和计算机框架的设计。

文本内容: It contains the design for firelock, air alarm, fire alarm, apc circuits and crap power cells.
翻译内容: 它包含了防火锁，空气报警器，火灾报警器，apc电路板和低质量电池的设计。

文本内容: It contains direct silo connection RCD upgrade.
翻译内容: 它包含直接链接矿物筒仓的RCD升级。

文本内容: It contains the design for chairs, stools, tables, and glass tables.
翻译内容: 它包含椅子、凳子、桌子和玻璃桌的设计。

文本内容: Scans the surrounding area for destruction. Scanned structures will rebuild significantly faster.
翻译内容: 扫描周围的区域的损坏，扫描后的结构将大大加快其重建速度。

文本内容: A device used to rapidly deploy pipe cleaners. It has screws on the side which can be removed to slide off the pipe cleaners. Do not use without insulation!
翻译内容: 一种用于快速部署管道清洁器的装置。它的侧面有螺丝，可以拆卸下来，从管道清洁器上滑动，请勿在没有绝缘材料的情况下使用！

文本内容: A banner with Nanotrasen's logo on it.
翻译内容: 一面印有纳米传讯标识的旗帜

文本内容: The banner of Securistan, ruling the station with an iron fist.
翻译内容: 安保的旗帜，太空站的铁腕统治。

文本内容: The banner of Meditopia, generous benefactors that cure wounds and shelter the weak.
翻译内容: 医疗的旗帜，慷慨的行善者治愈创伤，庇护弱者

文本内容: The banner of Sciencia, bold and daring thaumaturges and researchers that take the path less traveled.
翻译内容: 科学的旗帜，大胆无畏的科学家和研究人员会走很少有人走过的路。

文本内容: The banner of the eternal Cargonia, with the mystical power of conjuring any object into existence.
翻译内容: 永恒的货舱之旗，拥有召唤任何物体的神秘力量。

文本内容: The banner of Engitopia, wielders of limitless power.
翻译内容: 工程托皮亚的旗帜，无限权力的持有者。

文本内容: The banner of Command, a staunch and ancient line of bueraucratic kings and queens.
翻译内容: 指挥的旗帜，坚定而古老的官僚国王和女王的队伍。

文本内容: A banner with the logo of the red deity.
翻译内容: 一面印有红色神灵标志的旗帜。

文本内容: A banner with the logo of the blue deity.
翻译内容: 有蓝色神灵标志的旗帜。

文本内容: It's a backpack with lots of extra room.  A banner with Nanotrasen's logo is attached, that can't be removed.
翻译内容: 这是一个有很多额外空间的背包，带有纳米传讯公司徽标的旗帜是不能移除的。

文本内容: It's a backpack with lots of extra room.  A red banner is attached, that can't be removed.
翻译内容: 这是一个有很多额外空间的背包，附在上面的红色旗帜是不能移除的。

文本内容: It's a backpack with lots of extra room.  A blue banner is attached, that can't be removed.
翻译内容: 这是一个有很多额外空间的背包，附在上面的蓝色旗帜是不能移除的。
一顶看起来和宗教有关的帽子。

文本内容: They're like gloves, but made of metal.
翻译内容: 它们就像手套，不过是金属做的。

文本内容: A rusted claymore, once at the heart of a powerful scottish clan struck down and oppressed by tyrants, it has been passed down the ages as a symbol of defiance.
翻译内容: 一把锈迹斑斑的苏格兰阔刃大剑，曾经是一个被暴君镇压的强大苏格兰家族的核心武器，它作为抗争的象征代代相传。

文本内容: A device used to rapidly pipe things.
翻译内容: 一种用于快速输送东西的装置。
快速管道分配器高级设计磁盘

文本内容: Adds reverse wrench mode to the RPD. Attention, due to budget cuts, the mode is hard linked to the destroy mode control button.
翻译内容: 增加扳手模式的RPD，注意，由于预算削减，这个模式强制连接到破坏模式控制按钮。

文本内容: A device used to rapidly deploy service items.
翻译内容: 用于快速部署服务事项的设备。

文本内容: A self-recharging device used to rapidly deploy cookies.
翻译内容: 一种用于快速部署曲奇饼干的自充电设备。
用来在周围传送的卷轴。

文本内容: \"Top Secret\" Nanotrasen documents, filled with complex diagrams and lists of names, dates and coordinates.
翻译内容: 纳米传讯\"最高机密\"文件，满是复杂的图表、名称、日期、坐标。

文本内容: \"Top Secret\" documents detailing sensitive Syndicate operational intelligence.
翻译内容: 辛迪加\"最高机密\"文件上详细记载了敏感作战情报。

文本内容: \"Top Secret\" documents detailing sensitive Syndicate operational intelligence. These documents are verified with a red wax seal.
翻译内容: 辛迪加\"最高机密\"文件上详细记载了敏感作战情报，这些文件有红色的认证封蜡。

文本内容: \"Top Secret\" documents detailing sensitive Syndicate operational intelligence. These documents are verified with a blue wax seal.
翻译内容: 辛迪加\"最高机密\"文件上详细记载了敏感作战情报，这些文件有蓝色的认证封蜡。

文本内容: \"Top Secret\" documents detailing Syndicate plasma mining operations.
翻译内容: 辛迪加\"最高机密\"文件上记载了等离子采矿作业详情。

文本内容: A copy of some top-secret documents. Nobody will notice they aren't the originals... right?
翻译内容: 一些绝密文件的副本，没人会注意到它们不是原品……对吧?

文本内容: A block that makes things sharp.
翻译内容: 一块可以让刀具变得锋利的石头
[desc] 至少, 它曾经是这样的。

文本内容: A block that will make your weapon sharper than Einstein on adderall.
翻译内容: 一块让你的刀具磨了之后变得比吃了安非他命的爱因斯坦更强大的磨刀石.

文本内容: A shield adept at blocking blunt objects from connecting with the torso of the shield wielder.
翻译内容: 一块擅长阻挡钝器的盾牌，与持有者的躯干相连接

文本内容: Bears an inscription on the inside: \"Romanes venio domus\".
翻译内容: 内侧刻有：\“罗马人要回家了\”。

文本内容: Bears an inscription on the inside: \"Romanes venio domus\". It appears to be a bit flimsy.
翻译内容: 内侧刻有：\“罗马人要回家了\”，似乎有点脆弱。
一种中世纪的由木头制成的圆盾

文本内容: A shield with a built in, high intensity light capable of blinding and disorienting suspects. Takes regular handheld flashes as bulbs.
翻译内容: 一种带有内置高强度灯光的盾牌，能够使嫌疑人致盲和迷失方向，使用常规手持闪光灯用作灯泡

文本内容: A shield that reflects almost all energy projectiles, but is useless against physical attacks. It can be retracted, expanded, and stored anywhere.
翻译内容: 一种几乎能反射所有能量投射物的盾牌，但对物理攻击无效，它可以收缩、展开，在收缩状态下可以存储在大部分地方

文本内容: An advanced riot shield made of lightweight materials that collapses for easy storage.
翻译内容: 一种高级的防暴盾牌，用更轻的物质制作，具有伸缩功能方便储存

文本内容: A shooting target that looks like syndicate scum.
翻译内容: 一个看上去像是那些辛迪加人渣的射击标靶

文本内容: A shooting target that looks like a xenomorphic alien.
翻译内容: 一个看上去像是那些异型怪物的射击标靶

文本内容: A shooting target that looks like a useless clown.
翻译内容: 一个看上去像是那些废物小丑的射击标靶

文本内容: A high tech picket sign used by silicons that can reprogram its surface at will. Probably hurts to get hit by, too.
翻译内容: 硅基生物使用的高科技示威牌，可以随意对其表面进行重新编程，被这玩意打中大概很痛

文本内容: The pinnacle of close combat technology, the hammer harnesses the power of a miniaturized singularity to deal crushing blows.
翻译内容: 作为近战技术的巅峰，这把锤子利用微型奇点的力量来进行致命打击

文本内容: A weapon worthy of a god, able to strike with the force of a lightning bolt. It crackles with barely contained energy.
翻译内容: 一把只有神配得上的武器，能够用闪电的力量打击目标，它发出的爆裂声几乎没有能量

文本内容: A haphazardly-constructed yet still deadly weapon of ancient design.
翻译内容: 一种结构随意但仍然致命的设计古老的武器。

文本内容: A makeshift spear with [G] attached to it
翻译内容: 一把临时制作的长矛，上面绑着一个 [G]

文本内容: Recovered from the aftermath of a revolt aboard Defense Outpost Theta Aegis, in which a seemingly endless tide of Assistants caused heavy casualities among Nanotrasen military forces.
翻译内容: 从西塔·宙斯盾防御前哨站叛乱后恢复，在这场叛乱中，似乎无穷无尽的助手部队造成了纳米传讯军队的严重伤亡。

文本内容: A haphazardly-constructed yet still deadly weapon. The pinnacle of modern technology.
翻译内容: 一种结构随意但仍然致命的武器，现代技术的顶峰

文本内容: A haphazardly-constructed bamboo stick with a sharpened tip, ready to poke holes into unsuspecting people.
翻译内容: 一根简单削尖了的竹竿，有一个锋利的尖端，可以在毫无戒备的人身上戳几个洞出来

文本内容: Offically branded 'pin the tail on the corgi' style party implement. Not intended to be used on people.
翻译内容: ‘把尾巴钉在柯基身上’官方品牌风格的派对用具，本品不适用于人体。

文本内容: pin the tail on the corgi
The rules are simple, pin the tail on the corgi, while blindfolded. Are you a bad enough dude to hit the target?
翻译内容: 规则很简单，蒙上眼睛，同时把尾巴钉在柯基身上，你足够坏到能正中目标吗?

文本内容: Place it on a wall to start playing pin the tail on the corgi.
翻译内容: 把它放在墙上，然后开始玩尾巴钉柯基。

文本内容: Tastes things, so you don't have to!
翻译内容: 它替你品尝东西，这样你就不用亲自这么做了！

文本内容: Used to track portable teleportation beacons and targets with embedded tracking implants.
翻译内容: 用于追踪带有嵌入式追踪植入物的便携式传送信标或目标。

文本内容: A portable item using blue-space technology. One of the buttons opens a portal, the other re-opens your last destination.
翻译内容: 使用蓝空技术的便携式传送器，使用其中一个按钮选择传送地点打开一道传送门，另一个按钮则负责快速打开您的上一个目的地

文本内容: A reverse-engineered version of the Nanotrasen portable handheld teleporter. Lacks the advanced safety features of its counterpart. A three-headed serpent can be seen on the back.
翻译内容: 一种逆向工程版本的纳米传讯便携式手持传送器，缺乏同类产品先进的安全性，在它的背面可以看到一条三头蛇。
放射性极强，戴好护目镜。
放射性物体的固体容器。

文本内容: A screwdriver with an ultra thin tip that's carefully designed to boost screwing speed.
翻译内容: 一种带有超薄尖端的螺丝刀，经过精心设计，可提高拧入速度。

文本内容: A large storage cluster consisting of multiple HDDs for usage in dedicated storage systems.
翻译内容: 由多个硬盘驱动器组成的大型存储集群，用于专用的存储系统。
研发服务器硬盘驱动器

文本内容: For some reason, people really seem to want to steal this. The source code on this drive is probably used for something awful!
翻译内容: 出于某种原因，人们似乎真的很想偷走它，这个驱动器上的源代码可能被用来做一些可怕的事情!

文本内容: A tiny, highly volatile sliver of a supermatter crystal. Do not handle without protection!
翻译内容: 一种微小的、高度易挥发的超物质晶体银。不要在没有保护的情况下操作！

文本内容: A tiny receptacle that releases an inert hyper-noblium mix upon sealing, allowing a sliver of a supermatter crystal to be safely stored.
翻译内容: 一个微小的容器，密封后释放出惰性的超铌混合物，从而可以安全地储存一小块超物质晶体

文本内容: A scalpel with a fragile tip of condensed hyper-noblium gas, searingly cold to the touch, that can safely shave a sliver off a supermatter crystal.
翻译内容: 一把手术刀，刀尖上有一个脆弱的固态铌刀头，摸起来很冷，可以安全地从超物质晶体上刮下一小块

文本内容: A pair of tongs made from condensed hyper-noblium gas, searingly cold to the touch, that can safely grip a supermatter sliver.
翻译内容: 一把由固态铌制成的钳子，摸起来很冷，可以安全地夹住超物质碎片

文本内容: A translucent balloon. There's nothing in it.
翻译内容: 半透明气球。里面什么都没有。

文本内容: A translucent balloon with some form of liquid sloshing around in it.
翻译内容: 一个半透明的气球，里面有某种形式的液体在晃动。

文本内容: A translucent balloon with some form of liquid sloshing around in it.
翻译内容: 一种半透明的气球，里面有某种液体在四处晃动。

文本内容: No birthday is complete without it.
翻译内容: 没有它的生日是不完整的。

文本内容: A balloon with a corgi face on it. For the all year good boys.
翻译内容: 一个画着柯基脸的气球，献给年度好孩子们。

文本内容: There is a tag on the back that reads \"FUK NT!11!\".
翻译内容: 气球的背面上有一个标签，上面写着\"操你妈的NT!11!\"

文本内容: A half inflated balloon about a boyband named Arreyst that was popular about ten years ago, famous for making fun of red jumpsuits as unfashionable.
翻译内容: 关于一个大约在十年前很受欢迎的'Arreyst'男子乐队的半充气气球,他们以开红连衣裙不时髦的玩笑而闻名

文本内容: Every captain's greatest ally when exploring the vast emptiness of space, now with a color display!
翻译内容: 是每一位舰长在探索广阔太空时最伟大的盟友，现在有了彩色显示器！

文本内容: A copy of the first run of Captain's Aid ever released. Functionally the same as the later batches, just more expensive. For the truly aristocratic.
翻译内容: 首批舰长小帮手的副本，功能上和之后的批次相同，只是更昂贵，属于真正的贵族。

文本内容: Looks almost like the real thing! Ages 8 and up. Please recycle in an autolathe when you're out of caps.
翻译内容: 十分逼真！8岁及以上。当你用完软弹时，请在自动车床中回收。

文本内容: Make sure to recyle the box in an autolathe when it gets empty.
翻译内容: 请确保回收到自动车床中时，盒子是空的

文本内容: A cheap, plastic replica of an energy sword. Realistic sounds! Ages 8 and up.
翻译内容: 一种能量剑的廉价塑料复制品。声音逼真！8岁及以上。

文本内容: It says \"Sternside Changs #1 fan\" on it.
A replica toolbox that rumbles when you turn the key.
翻译内容: 这是一个仿制的工具箱，当你转动发条时会发出可怖的声音

文本内容: A cheap, plastic replica of TWO energy swords.  Double the fun!
翻译内容: 这是两根能量剑的便宜仿制品！双倍快乐！
遗憾的是，他并没有被D20赐予实际的力量

文本内容: A generic action figure modeled after nothing in particular.
翻译内容: 一个没什么特点的普通活动人偶。

文本内容: A little toy model AI core with real law announcing action!
翻译内容: 一个小的AI核心玩具模型！会像真的一样公告法律！

文本内容: A tool to help you write fictional devils!
翻译内容: 一个工具，帮助你写出虚构的恶魔！

文本内容: An action figure modeled after 'The Owl', defender of justice.
翻译内容: 一个以‘猫头鹰’为原型的活动玩偶，是正义的捍卫者。

文本内容: An action figure modeled after 'The Griffin', criminal mastermind.
翻译内容: 一个模仿‘狮鹫’的人偶，犯罪策划大师。

文本内容: A plastic model of a Nuclear Fission Explosive.
翻译内容: 核裂变炸药的塑料模型。

文本内容: Relive the excitement of a meteor shower! SweetMeat-eor Co. is not responsible for any injuries, headaches or hearing loss caused by Mini-Meteor.
翻译内容: 重温令人兴奋的流星雨！蜜饯公司对迷你陨石造成的任何伤害、头痛或听力损失不负任何责任。

文本内容: A big, plastic red button. Reads 'From HonkCo Pranks!' on the back.
翻译内容: 一个大大的红色塑料按钮，背面写着‘来自洪克公司的恶作剧！’。

文本内容: A compact ball of snow. Good for throwing at people.
翻译内容: 一团紧密的雪。很适合用来扔向人。

文本内容: The simple beach ball is one of Nanotrasen's most popular products. 'Why do we make beach balls? Because we can! (TM)' - Nanotrasen
翻译内容: 这种简单的沙滩球是纳米传讯最受欢迎的产品之一，‘我们为什么要做沙滩球?因为我们能做！(版权所有)’——纳米传讯

文本内容: Enter the world of concussions and become who you were destined to be.
翻译内容: 进入脑震荡的世界，成为你注定要成为的人。

文本内容: A stylish steampunk watch made out of thousands of tiny cogwheels.
翻译内容: 一个时髦的蒸汽朋克手表，由成千上万个小齿轮组成。

文本内容: A cheap plastic replica of a dagger. Produced by THE ARM Toys, Inc.
翻译内容: 一个廉价的塑料匕首复制品，由大臂玩具公司生产。

文本内容: MEGA presents the new Xenos Isolated action figure! Comes complete with realistic sounds! Pull back string to use.
翻译内容: MEGA推出了全新的异形独立动作人偶！可以发出相当真实的声音！拉回绳子使用它。
一只五颜六色的玩具老鼠！
没有特定动作的活动人偶

文本内容: May you always have a shell in your pocket and sand in your shoes. Whatever that's supposed to mean.
翻译内容: 愿你口袋里永远有贝壳，鞋子里永远有沙子，管它什么意思。

文本内容: An old radio that produces nothing but static when turned on.
翻译内容: 一个旧收音机，打开之后只会有静电声

文本内容: A Mr. Monstrous brand toy made to imitate a human brain in smell and texture.
翻译内容: 怪兽先生牌玩具，在气味和质地上模仿人脑

文本内容: A toy book that closely resembles the Codex Cicatrix. Covered in fake polyester human flesh and has a huge goggly eye attached to the cover. The runes are gibberish and cannot be used to summon demons... Hopefully?
翻译内容: 一本玩具书，很像瘢痕法典，上面覆盖着人造聚酯人肉，还有一只巨大的眼睛附在封面上，这些符文都是胡言乱语，不能用来召唤恶魔……也许?

文本内容: Hah. You thought it was the real deal!
A box containing toys resembling pierced realities.
翻译内容: 一个盒子，里面装着像刺穿的现实一样的玩具。

文本内容: root for the home team! wait, does this station even have a sports team?
翻译内容: 为主场队加油！等等，这个空间站有运动队吗?

文本内容: Fundamentally useless for all intentsive purposes.
翻译内容: 从根本上说对所有有意的目的都毫无用处。
暗黑 H.O.N.K 机甲玩具
胆小鬼的私人储备牛肉干
这玩意根本就是个垃圾！

文本内容: a picture of the virgin mary
A small, cheap icon depicting the virgin mother.
翻译内容: 一个描绘圣母的廉价小画像。

文本内容: Looks like a circuit. Probably is.

翻译内容: 美味，散发着干酪香味，而且热的时候更好吃。

文本内容: The award-winning donk-pocket that won the hearts of clowns and humans alike.
翻译内容: 小丑和人类都喜欢的获奖口袋饼。

文本内容: The award-winning donk-pocket, now warm and toasty.
翻译内容: 获奖的口袋饼，现在又热乎又温暖。

文本内容: A relentlessly sweet donk-pocket first created for use in Operation Dessert Storm.
翻译内容: 为甜品风暴行动（Operation Dessert Storm）而创造出的一款甜味十足的口袋饼。

文本内容: A relentlessly sweet donk-pocket, now warm and delicious.
翻译内容: 一款甜味十足的口袋饼，现在又热乎又美味。

文本内容: The choice to use real gondola meat in the recipe is controversial, to say the least.
翻译内容: 退一步来说，在食谱中选择使用真正的贡多拉肉是有争议的。

文本内容: The choice to use real gondola meat in the recipe is controversial, to say the least.
翻译内容: 退一步来说，在食谱中选择使用真正的贡多拉肉是有争议的。

文本内容: Like life, it never quite tastes the same.
翻译内容: 就像生活，它的味道永不重样。

文本内容: Tastes as gross as it looks.
Goes great with a soy latte.
Goes great with a cold beaker of malk.
翻译内容: 与一杯冰凉的麦芽饮料搭配非常美味

文本内容: Goes great with a shot of cinnamon schnapps.
翻译内容: 如果配上一杯肉桂杜松子酒就更好了。

文本内容: Goes great with a mug of hot coco.
Goes great with a glass of warm milk.
Goes great with a mug of soothing drunken blumpkin.
Goes great with a mason jar of hippie's delight.
Goes great with a cup of tea.
Goes great with a bottle of Bastion Burbon!
翻译内容: 与一瓶堡垒波本威士忌搭配非常棒！

Goes great with a cold beaker of malk.

翻译内容: 与一杯冰凉的麦芽饮料搭配非常美味

文本内容: Goes great with a mug of hot coco.

Goes great with a mason jar of hippie's delight.
Goes great with a cup of tea.
Goes great with a bottle of Bastion Burbon!

文本内容: Add ingredients to make a pizza.
翻译内容: 需要加入配料来做披萨。

文本内容: A slice of dough. Can be cooked into a bun.
翻译内容: 切成块的面团。可以制作成圆面包。

文本内容: A base for any self-respecting burger.
翻译内容: 是任何有自尊的汉堡的基础。

文本内容: Bake it to get a cake.
翻译内容: 烤一下就可以做蛋糕了。

文本内容: Cook it to get a pie.
翻译内容: 把它煮熟就能得到一个馅饼。

文本内容: A base for any self-respecting pastry.
翻译内容: 是任何有自尊的糕点的基础。
这种甜美的、使人发胖的食物。
一颗蛋哦！看起来好诡异……

文本内容: An egg that has been decorated with the grotesque, robustable likeness of a clown's face.
翻译内容: 一个有怪诞、粗壮小丑脸肖像的鸡蛋。

文本内容: A fried egg. Would go well with a touch of salt and pepper.
翻译内容: 一颗煎蛋。配一点盐和胡椒会很不错。

文本内容: Supposedly good for you, if you can stomach it. Better fried.
翻译内容: 据说对你有好处，如果你能忍受的话，最好是油炸的。

文本内容: A good egg with a side of sausages.
翻译内容: 一个不错的鸡蛋配上香肠。

文本内容: There is only one egg on this, how rude.
翻译内容: 这上面只有一个鸡蛋，真粗鲁。

文本内容: The precursor to Pigs in a Blanket.
A legendary egg custard that makes friends out of enemies. Probably too hot for a cat to eat.
翻译内容: 一种传奇的炖蛋，能化敌为友，可能太烫了，猫吃不了。

文本内容: Portable Ice-cream in its own packaging.
翻译内容: 自带包装的便携式冰激凌。

文本内容: Portable ice-cream in its own packaging of the strawberry variety.
翻译内容: 自带包装的便携式草莓冰激凌。

文本内容: It's just shaved ice. Still fun to chew on.
翻译内容: 只是单纯的刨冰而已。但吃起来还是很有趣的。

文本内容: Lime syrup drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有酸橙糖浆的刨冰。

文本内容: Lemon syrup drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有柠檬糖浆的刨冰。

文本内容: Apple syrup drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有苹果糖浆的刨冰。

文本内容: Grape syrup drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有葡萄糖浆的刨冰。

文本内容: Orange syrup drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有橙子糖浆的刨冰。

文本内容: Bluecherry syrup drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup, how rare!
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有蓝樱桃糖浆的刨冰，好稀奇！

文本内容: Cherry syrup drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有樱桃糖浆的刨冰。

文本内容: Berry syrup drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有浆果糖浆的刨冰。

文本内容: A delightful mix of citrus syrups drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
Pineapple syrup drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有菠萝糖浆的刨冰。

文本内容: Laughter drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有笑声的刨冰。

文本内容: Space Cola drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有太空可乐的刨冰。

文本内容: Space Mountain Wind drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有太空山风的刨冰。

文本内容: Pwrgame soda drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有头号玩家的刨冰。

文本内容: Honey drizzled over a snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着淋有蜂蜜的刨冰。

文本内容: A very colorful snowball in a paper cup.
翻译内容: 纸杯中放着一份五颜六色的刨冰。

文本内容: This humble little stick usually carries a frozen treat, at the moment it seems freed from this Atlassian burden.
翻译内容: 这根不起眼的小棍子通常背负着一种冰冻的食物，现在它似乎摆脱了这个沉重的负担。

文本内容: A classic orange creamsicle. A sunny frozen treat.
翻译内容: 经典的橙色奶油雪糕，阳光明媚的冰冻甜点。

文本内容: A vibrant berry creamsicle. A berry good frozen treat.
翻译内容: 充满活力的浆果奶油雪糕，一种浆果味的冰冻甜点。

文本内容: A luxurious icecream covered in rich chocolate. It seems smaller than you remember it being.
翻译内容: 一种覆盖着浓郁巧克力的奢华冰淇淋，但它看起来比你记忆中要小。

文本内容: A salty licorice icecream. A salty frozen treat.
翻译内容: 一种咸的甘草冰淇淋，一个有咸味的冷冻点心。

文本内容: A neapolitan vanilla and chocolate icecream cone. It menaces with a sprinkling of caramelized nuts.
翻译内容: 那不勒斯香草与巧克力制成的冰淇淋蛋筒，它上面撒有焦糖坚果。

文本内容: A raw Tiziran blood sausage, ready to be cured on a drying rack.
翻译内容: 一根生的蜥蜴式血肠，准备放在烘干架上晒干。

文本内容: A coarse dry-cured blood sausage, traditionally made by farmers in the farmlands around Zagoskeld. Similar in texture to old-Earth Spanish chorizo.
翻译内容: 一种粗糙的干制血肠，传统上由蜥德里郊区的农民制作，质地类似于旧地球的西班牙香肠。

文本内容: A common food on Tizira, headcheese is traditionally made of an animal's head, with the organs removed, boiled until it falls apart, at which point it is collected, strained of moisture, salted heavily, packed into blocks, and left to dry and age for several months. The resulting hard block tastes similar to cheese.
翻译内容: 作为蜥蜴人的一种常见食物，头肉冻传统上是由动物的头部制成的，去掉器官，煮到分崩离析，然后收集起来，过滤水分，重盐调味然后包装成块，放在干燥的地方陈化几个月，由此产生的硬块尝起来与奶酪相似。

文本内容: A cured block of headcheese. Delicious, if you're a lizard.
翻译内容: 一块腌制好的头肉冻，美味，如果你是一只蜥蜴的话。

文本内容: A slice of headcheese, useful for making sandwiches and snacks. Or surviving the cold Tiziran winters.
翻译内容: 一片切好的头肉冻，可以用来做三明治和小吃，或者在寒冷的提兹兰冬天幸存下来。

文本内容: Crispy lung strips, with veggies and a spicy sauce. Delicious, if you like lungs.
翻译内容: 脆肺条，配蔬菜和辣酱，美味，如果你喜欢肺的话。

文本内容: A Tiziran dish consisting of spiced ground offal, stuffed into a stomach and boiled. Pretty foul to anyone who's not used to the taste.
翻译内容: 一种蜥蜴人菜，将香料和碎内脏塞进胃里煮熟而成，对任何不习惯这种味道的人来说都是相当难吃的。

文本内容: A rich, meaty paste made from liver, meat, and a few additions for extra flavour.
翻译内容: 一种油腻的，用肝脏和肉以及其他增添风味的配料制作而成的肉酱

文本内容: The moonfish lays large, transparent white eggs which are prized in lizard cooking. Their flavour is similar to caviar, but generally is described as deeper and more complex.
翻译内容: 月鱼产下的大而透明的白色卵，在蜥蜴菜系中很受欢迎，它们的味道类似鱼子酱，但通常被描述为更加复杂和深层次的味道

文本内容: A rich paste made from moonfish eggs. Generally the only way most lizards can get them, and used fairly heavily in coastal cooking.
翻译内容: 月鱼鱼子制成的浓稠糊状物。一般来说，这是大多数蜥蜴获取它们的唯一途径，在沿海地区中被大量使用

文本内容: Another example of cultural crossover between lizards and humans, desert snail escargot is closer to the Roman dish cocleas than the contemporary French escargot. It's a common street food in the desert cities.
翻译内容: 一个蜥蜴和人类文化交融的优秀例子，这道沙漠蜗牛比当代法国蜗牛更接近罗马菜，沙漠城市常见的街头食品

文本内容: A blood sausage, battered and deep fried. Commonly served with fries as a quick and simple snack on the streets of Zagoskeld.
翻译内容: 一条血肠，打碎后油炸，在扎戈斯克尔德的街道上，通常与炸薯条一起作为一种简单快捷的小吃

文本内容: One of the many human foods to make its way to the lizards was french fries, which are called poms-franzisks in Draconic. When topped with barbecued meat and sauce, they make a hearty meal.
翻译内容: 条条人类食谱中通向蜥蜴人菜系的食物之一是薯条，这种食物被称为肉酱薯条，当上面有烤肉和酱汁时，它们就是一顿丰盛的晚餐。

文本内容: A thick pink puree made from finely chopped poached eyeballs and brains, fried onions, and fat. Lizards swear it's delicious!
翻译内容: 一种由切碎的水煮眼球和脑、炸洋葱和脂肪制成的粉红糊状物，蜥蜴发誓它很好吃！

文本内容: A delicious snack from the streets of Zagoskeld, consisting of headcheese coated in rootbread breadcrumbs. Commonly served with fries.
翻译内容: 一种来自蜥德里街头的美味小吃，由裹着面包屑的头肉冻组成，通常与薯条一起食用。

文本内容: A popular Tiziran streetfood consisting of vinegar-marinated armorfish on a skewer with onion and chillis.
翻译内容: 一种受欢迎的蜥蜴人街头小吃，用醋腌制的装甲鱼放在串着洋葱和辣椒的铁钎上。

文本内容: Little crispy larvae in a korta nectar based sweet and spicy sauce. Bugtastic!
翻译内容: 一些看起来小但口感很脆的幼虫浸泡在以科尔塔花蜜为基础的甜辣酱中，虫子味！

文本内容: A medley of mushrooms, made to meet your monstrous munchies. Marvelous!
翻译内容: 蘑菇大杂烩，专为满足你深不见底的食欲而来，精彩！

文本内容: A slab of grilled moonfish. Traditionally served over scalloped roots with a wine-based sauce.
翻译内容: 一大块烤月鱼，传统方法是佐以浇上葡萄酒酱汁的扇贝根食用。

文本内容: A slab of beautifully seared moonfish on a bed of potatoes and carrots, with a wine and demiglace reduction on top. Simply marvelous.
翻译内容: 一块精美的烤月鱼放在土豆和胡萝卜上，上面是葡萄酒和半冰牛排，真是太棒了。

文本内容: A massive platter of Tizira's finest meat and seafood, typically shared by groups at the beach. Of course, nothing's stopping you eating it on your own... fatass.
翻译内容: 一大盘蜥蜴人认为最好的肉和海鲜，通常是海滩上的人同享的，当然，没有什么能阻止你自己一个人把它吃光，肥仔。

文本内容: A form of root and nut pasta originally native to the oceanside regions of Tizira. It's similar in texture and appearance to gnocchi.
A high class pasta dish from Tizira's vineyard region of Valyngia. Traditionally made with only the finest Tiziran wine... but the human swill will do, in a pinch.
A lizard adaptation of the Italian pasta dish, aglio e olio, made with nizaya pasta.
A sweet, creamy nizaya pasta dish made with korta milk and nectar.
A nizaya pasta dish made with seraka mushrooms and quality oil. Has a pronounced nutty flavour.
A root based dough, made with nuts and tubers. Used in a wide range of Tiziran cooking.
Flattened rootdough, ready to be made into a flatbread, or cut into segments.
翻译内容: 压扁的粗面团，可以做成面饼，或切成小段。

文本内容: A ball of root dough. Perfect for making pasta or rolls.
翻译内容: 一团粗面团，非常适合做意大利面或面包卷。

文本内容: A plain grilled root flatbread. Can be topped with a variety of foods that lizards like to eat.
翻译内容: 一个普通的烤粗面饼，上面可以放蜥蜴喜欢吃的各种食物。

文本内容: A dense, chewy roll, made from roots. A nice companion to a bowl of soup.
翻译内容: 粗面卷，一种由块茎和坚果制成的密实而有嚼劲的卷是一碗汤的绝佳伴侣。

文本内容: The lizard equivalent to bread, made from tubers like potatoes and yams mixed with ground nuts and seeds. Noticably denser than regular bread.
翻译内容: 这种食物相当于蜥蜴的面包，由土豆和山药等块茎混合坚果和植物种子制成，密度明显大于普通面包。

文本内容: A slice of dense, chewy rootbread.
A simple Tiziran country dish, popular as a side to meat or fish dishes. Topped with herbs and oil.
翻译内容: 一种简单的蜥蜴人乡村菜，常作为肉或鱼的配菜，上面撒上香料和油。

文本内容: The introduction of human foods to Tizira led to an advancement in lizard cooking- the Italic flatbread is now a common sight on the menus of takeout stores on the planet.
翻译内容: 人类的食物被引入蜥蜴人的食谱后，蜥蜴人们的烹饪技术更进一步——意大利烤饼现在在地球上的外卖店菜单上很常见了。

文本内容: A flatbread topped with pate, pickled vegetables, and cubed headcheese. Not very suited to anyone's tastes but the lizards.
翻译内容: 一种上面有肉酱、腌蔬菜和切成块状的干酪的大饼，除了蜥蜴人，不太适合其他任何人的口味。

文本内容: A popular sandwich on Tizira, named in honour of the Imperial family.
翻译内容: 蜥蜴人中一种受欢迎的三明治，以皇室的名字命名。

文本内容: A sweetened rootroll with sliced fruit, enjoyed as a seasonal dessert on Tizira.
翻译内容: 一种把加糖的粗面卷和切好的水果一起烹饪的菜品，作为蜥蜴人的应季甜点。

文本内容: A bowl of rich, meaty dumpling soup, traditionally served during the festival of Atrakor's Might on Tizira. The dumplings are shaped like the Night Sky Lord himself.
A hearty noodle soup made from meatballs and nizaya in a rich broth. Commonly topped with a handful of chopped nuts.
A bowl of sausage, onion, blood and vinegar, served ice cold. Every bit as rough as it sounds.
A slimy bowl of jellyfish stew. It jiggles if you shake it.
翻译内容: 一碗黏糊糊的炖水母，如果你摇晃它，它就会不停抖动。

文本内容: A big bowl of spicy, savoury soup made with rootbread. Heavily seasoned, and very tasty.
翻译内容: 用根面包做的一大碗辛辣可口的汤，口味很重，但非常美味。

文本内容: A country dish from rural Tizira. Made with eggs, blood, and foraged greens. Traditionally eaten with rootbread and a spicy sauce.
翻译内容: 来自蜥蜴人乡村的一道充满乡土味的菜肴，它是用鸡蛋，血液和蔬菜做成的，传统吃法是搭配上粗面包和辣酱。

文本内容: A smooth and spicy tomato-based sauce topped with eggs and baked. Delicious.
A big slab of korta nut brittle. So sugary it should be a crime!
翻译内容: 一大块科尔塔果仁脆糖。太甜了，简直就是犯罪!

文本内容: A little slice of korta nut brittle. A diabetic's worst enemy.
翻译内容: 一小片科尔塔果仁脆糖。糖尿病患者的头号大敌。

文本内容: Shaved ice, korta nectar and berries. A sweet treat to eat to beat summer heat!
翻译内容: 一种消暑的甜食！原料是刨冰，科尔塔花蜜和浆果。

文本内容: A slightly bizarre dish from Tizira, consisting of seraka mushrooms coated with caramel on a skewer. Carries a pronounced 'sweet and savoury' kick.
翻译内容: 这是来自蜥蜴人的一种略显奇怪的菜肴，由涂有焦糖的蘑菇串成，带有明显的‘甜味和咸味’。

文本内容: Pickled cabbage, as made famous by Germans, and which has become common in lizard cooking, where it is known as Zauerkrat.
Mashed root vegetables, mixed with korta flour and boiled to produce a large, round and slightly spicy dumpling. Commonly eaten in soup.
翻译内容: 捣碎的蔬菜根茎与科尔塔粉混合，煮成一个又大又圆，略带辣味的饺子。通常在汤里吃。

文本内容: Seraka mushrooms that have been steeped in alkaline water to remove the extract, thereby making them completely safe to consume.
A can of gunner jellyfish packed in brine. Contains a mild hallucinogen which is destroyed by cooking.
Giant snails from the Tiziran desert, packaged in brine. Shells included. Probably best not eaten raw, unless you're a lizard.
A can of bee larva packaged in honey. Probably appetizing to someone.
翻译内容: 用蜂蜜包装的一罐蜜蜂幼虫，可能对某人来说算是开胃菜。

文本内容: A grifftastic sandwich that burns your tongue and then leaves it numb!
翻译内容: 一个可怕的三明治，它会灼伤你的舌头，然后让它失去知觉!

文本内容: A fillet of some fish meat.
A fillet of spess carp meat.
Almost just like the real thing, kinda.
翻译内容: 几乎和真的一样，也许有一点吧。

文本内容: A gunner jellyfish with the stingers removed. Mildly hallucinogenic.
An armorfish with its guts and shell removed, ready for use in cooking.
The dreaded donkfish fillet. No sane spaceman would eat this, and it does not get better when cooked.
I do say so myself chap.
All that and no bag of chips...
A taco with fish, cheese, and cabbage.
翻译内容: 一份含有鱼、奶酪和卷心菜的塔可。

文本内容: A roll of simple vegetarian sushi with rice, carrots, and potatoes. Sliceable into pieces!
