翻译内容: 虽然烘烤过的种子远不能填饱肚子，但在蛾子中，它是一种很受欢迎的小吃。盐、糖，甚至一些更具异国情调的调味品都可以加，以增加风味。

文本内容: A common snack for engineers on the mothic fleet, made of seeds, nuts, chocolate, popcorn, and potato chips- designed to be dense with calories and easy to snack on when an extra boost is needed.
翻译内容: 这是一种为飞蛾舰队的工程师们准备的常见零食，由种子、坚果、巧克力、爆米花和薯片制成，其设计具有高热量，并且在需要额外补充营养时易于食用的特点。

文本内容: A strong, glutenous dough, made with cornmeal and flour, designed to hold up to cheese and sauce.
翻译内容: 一种用谷物粉和面粉制成的结实而有粘性的面团，用来吸收奶酪和酱汁

文本内容: A mothic classic made with cheese curds and tofu (amongst other things). Translated literally the name means 'squeaking stir fry', a name given due to the distinctive squeak of the proteins.
Grilled cheese and salad in a cabbage wrap, topped with delicious sweet chili sauce.
翻译内容: 烤奶酪和卷心菜卷沙拉，上面淋上了美味的甜辣椒酱。

文本内容: What's better than cheese curds? Deep fried cheese curds! What's better than deep fried cheese curds? Deep fried cheese curds with chili (and more cheese) on top! And what's better than that? Putting it on fries!
A baked cheese wheel, melty and delicious.
翻译内容: 一个烤奶酪轮，融汁四溢而美味

文本内容: A baked cheese wheel: a mothic favourite for sharing. Usually served with crispy bread slices for dipping, because the only thing better than good cheese is good cheese on bread.
A fine lasagne made with pesto and a herby white sauce, ready to bake. Good for multiple servings.
翻译内容: 用香蒜沙司和香草白酱做的美味千层面，适合多人食用。

文本内容: A fine lasagne made with pesto and a herby white sauce. Good for multiple servings.
翻译内容: 用香蒜沙司和香草白酱做的美味千层面，适合多人食用。

文本内容: A slice of herby, pesto-y lasagne.
翻译内容: 一片香草味的香蒜沙司千层面。

文本内容: A big pan of layered potatoes topped with rice and vegetable stock, ready to be baked into a delicious sharing meal.
翻译内容: 一大锅层状的土豆，上面有米饭和蔬菜高汤，准备烤成美味的合用餐。

文本内容: A mothic favourite, baked rice can be filled with a variety of vegetable fillings to make a delicious meal to share. Potatoes are also often layered on the bottom of the cooking vessel to create a flavourful crust which is hotly contested amongst diners.
翻译内容: 烤饭是蛾人们的最爱，可以用各种各样的蔬菜馅做一顿美味的饭来分享，土豆层经常分在烹饪容器的底部，烹饪成一个美味的外壳，这是食客们竞相争抢的美味。

文本内容: A single portion of baked rice, perfect as a side dish, or even as a full meal.
翻译内容: 一份烤米饭，是完美的配菜，甚至能当做正餐。

文本内容: A cob of corn, baked in the roasting heat of an oven until it blisters and blackens. Beloved as a quick yet flavourful and filling component for dishes on the Fleet.
翻译内容: 一根玉米棒，在烤箱的高温下烤至起泡变黑作为一种便捷而美味的食材，深受人们的喜爱。

文本内容: What's better than baked corn? Baked corn with butter!
翻译内容: 还有什么比烤玉米更好的呢？加黄油的烤玉米！

文本内容: Sweet, spicy, saucy, and all kinds of corny.
翻译内容: 甜蜜的，刺激的，香辣的，还有各种玉米。

文本内容: Sliced vegetables with a roasted pepper sauce. Delicious, for a peasant food.
翻译内容: 切片蔬菜配热煨辣椒酱，作为农家菜，相当美味。

文本内容: The perfect dish to save your restaurant from a vindictive food critic. Bonus points if you've got a rat in your hat.
翻译内容: 这道完美的菜能把你的餐厅从报复心强的美食评论家手中拯救出来，如果你的帽子里还有只老鼠，那更是个加分项。

文本内容: Little sticks of mozzarella, breaded and fried.
翻译内容: 小块马苏里拉奶酪，裹上面包屑，油炸

文本内容: A pepper with the top removed and a herby cheese and onion mix stuffed inside. Probably shouldn't be eaten raw.
A soft yet still crisp bell pepper, with a wonderful melty cheesy interior.
翻译内容: 柔软却不失清脆的甜椒，内部有着美妙的乳酪般的融化感。

文本内容: A dish made from fried vegetables, popular amongst fueljacks- the brave moths who operate the fuel skimmers to keep the fleet running. Given the constant need for fuel, and the limited windows in which the stars align for harvesting (literally), they'll often take packed meals to save on trips to the mess, which they heat using the fresh canisters.
翻译内容: 这道菜是用油炸蔬菜做成的，在燃油工人中很受欢迎，燃油工人是一群勇敢的飞蛾，他们操纵着燃油分离器，以保持舰队的运转，由于燃料供应需要持续不断，以及星星排在一排等待收获的时间(真的)很有限，他们通常会自带食物，用新的罐子加热，以节省去食堂的时间。

文本内容: Fried balls of macaroni cheese dipped in corn batter, served with tomato sauce. A popular snack across the galaxy, and especially on the Mothic Fleet- where they tend to use Ready-Donk as the base.

The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. This particular one is, like most artificially-flavoured moth food, mixed-herb flavoured.
翻译内容: PSB，或称预包装营养棒（Prepacked Sustenance Bar），是一种包装紧密、营养丰富的食物，为了让人们支撑过食物短缺而研发，它由大豆和豌豆蛋白制成，如果定量食用，每一支都能维持3天的营养消耗，虽然它们的保质期很长，但它们最终还是会变质——这促使它们作为剩余的的部分被舰队出售，这种特别的飞蛾食物，和大多数人工调味的飞蛾食物一样混合了药草来调味。
盈余舰队PSB- 那不勒斯风味

文本内容: The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. This particular one is neapolitan flavoured- strawberry, vanilla, and chocolate.
翻译内容: PSB，或称预包装营养棒（Prepacked Sustenance Bar），是一种包装紧密、营养丰富的食物，为了让人们支撑过食物短缺而研发，它由大豆和豌豆蛋白制成，如果定量食用，每一支都能维持3天的营养消耗，虽然它们的保质期很长，但它们最终还是会变质——这促使它们作为剩余的的部分被舰队出售，这款是特殊的那不勒斯风味的，混合了草莓、香草和巧克力。
盈余舰队PSB- 三奶酪风味

文本内容: The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. This particular one is three-cheese flavoured- parmesan, mozzarella, and cheddar.
翻译内容: PSB，或称预包装营养棒（Prepacked Sustenance Bar），是一种包装紧密、营养丰富的食物，为了让人们支撑过食物短缺而研发，它由大豆和豌豆蛋白制成，如果定量食用，每一支都能维持3天的营养消耗，虽然它们的保质期很长，但它们最终还是会变质——这促使它们作为剩余的的部分被舰队出售，这款是特殊的三奶酪风味——帕尔马干酪、马苏里拉奶酪和切达干酪。

文本内容: surplus fleet PSB- mint choc chip flavour
翻译内容: 盈余舰队PSB- 盈余舰队风味

文本内容: The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. This particular one is mint choc chip flavoured- peppermint, dark chocolate, and potato chips, showing that mothkind has no idea what mint choc chip is.
翻译内容: PSB，或称预包装营养棒（Prepacked Sustenance Bar），是一种包装紧密、营养丰富的食物，为了让人们支撑过食物短缺而研发，它由大豆和豌豆蛋白制成，如果定量食用，每一支都能维持3天的营养消耗，虽然它们的保质期很长，但它们最终还是会变质——这促使它们作为剩余的的部分被舰队出售，这款是特殊的薄荷巧克力片风味——薄荷、黑巧克力和薯片，这表明蛾族根本不知道薄荷巧克力片是什么。

文本内容: surplus fleet PSB- three course dinner

The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. This particular one is split into three flavours, making up a typical meal- tomato soup, roast pumpkin, and blueberry pie.
翻译内容: PSB，或称预包装营养棒（Prepacked Sustenance Bar），是一种包装紧密、营养丰富的食物，为了让人们支撑过食物短缺而研发，它由大豆和豌豆蛋白制成，如果定量食用，每一支都能维持3天的营养消耗，虽然它们的保质期很长，但它们最终还是会变质——这促使它们作为剩余的的部分被舰队出售，这款特殊的口味被分为三个部分，构成这经典一餐——番茄汤、烤南瓜和蓝莓派。

文本内容: A soup made from raw cotton in a flavourful vegetable broth. Enjoyed only by moths and the criminally tasteless.
A simple and filling soup made from homemade cheese and sweet potato. The curds provide texture while the whey provides volume- and they both provide deliciousness!
A seed based soup, made by germinating seeds and then boiling them. Produces a particularly bitter broth which is usually balanced by the addition of vinegar.
For the hombres who don't want carne.
A spicy bean stew with lots of veggies, commonly served aboard the fleet as a filling and satisfying meal with rice or bread.
A hearty oat stew, prepared with oats, sweet potatoes, and various winter vegetables.
Tömpröttkrakklmæsch, or heartburn soup, is a cold soup dish that originated amongst the jungle moths, and is named for two things- its rosy pink colour, and its scorchingly hot chilli heat.
A plate of rice porridge. It's mostly flavourless, but it does fill a spot. To the Chinese it's congee, and moths call it höllflöfmisklsløsk.
Nobody is quite sure why this smiley bowl of rice porridge with eggs and bacon is named after a mythological Chinese figure- it's just sorta what it's always been called.
Commonly served aboard the mothic fleet, rice porridge with töchtaüse syrup is more palatable than the regular stuff, if even just because it's spicier than normal.
A plate of cornmeal porridge. It's more flavourful than most porridges, and makes a good base for other flavours, too.
翻译内容: 一盘谷物粥，它比其他大多数的粥都好吃，也可以作为其他口味的好底料。

文本内容: A rich and creamy bowl of cheesy cornmeal porridge.
翻译内容: 一碗奶油浓郁的芝士玉米粥。

文本内容: Polenta loaded with cheese, served with a few discs of fried eggplant and some tomato sauce. Lække!

While it's far from an original creation of the moths, caprese salad has become a favourite aboard the Fleet due to how simple it is to prepare yet how tasty it is. To the moths it's known as zaileskenknusksolt: two tone salad, in GalCom.

Lörtonknusksolt, or Fleet Salad in GalCom, is commonly seen at the snack bars and canteens aboard the Fleet. The grilled cheese makes it particularly filling, while the croutons provide a crunchy kick.
A salad with added cotton and a basic dressing. Presumably either moths are around, or the South's risen again.
Originally a Kenyan recipe, kachumbari is yet another cross-cultural favourite from humanity that has been adopted by the moths- though some ingredients have been necessarily changed.
Another human classic adopted by the moths, mothic pizza is characterised by the use of fresh ingredients, particularly fresh mozzarella, and the use of strong flour to produce a glutenous dough.
A key characteristic of mothic pizza is that it's sold by weight- single slices are available for discretionary credits, while a meal ticket can buy a whole pie.
A slice of mothic margherita pizza, the most humble of pizzas.
A favourite amongst the more adventurous moths, firecracker pizza is HOT HOT HOT!
翻译内容: 爆竹披萨是飞蛾中更具冒险精神者的最爱，它很烫烫烫！

文本内容: They're not kidding when they call this a hot pizza pie.
翻译内容: 他们说这块披萨炙手可热，他们是认真的。

文本内容: A spicy slice of something quite nice.
For centuries, scholars have asked: how much cheese is too much cheese?
A favourite amongst mice, rats, and English inventors.
It's the cheesiest slice in the galaxy!
翻译内容: 这是全银河系最烂的奶酪片!

文本内容: A pizza made for the tomato haters.
翻译内容: 为讨厌番茄的人做的披萨。

文本内容: You say to-may-to, I say to-mah-to, and we put neither on this pizza.
翻译内容: 你说可-能-会-来，我说可-楞-会-来，然后我们就不会被放到披萨上了。
奶酪味，蒜味，香草味，美味!

文本内容: Pesto is a popular pizza topping for moths, quite possibly because it exemplifies their favourite flavours: cheese, herbs, and veggies.
翻译内容: 香蒜沙司是飞蛾喜爱的披萨配料，很可能是因为它代表了飞蛾最喜欢的几种食物：奶酪、香草和蔬菜。

文本内容: Green as the grass in the garden. Not that there's many of those on mothic ships.
翻译内容: 像花园里的草一样绿，虽然有蛾类的船上很少有这种东西。

文本内容: A slice of presto pesto pizza.
Ahh, garlic. A universally loved ingredient, except possibly by vampires.
翻译内容: 啊，大蒜。一种广受欢迎的配料，可能吸血鬼除外。

文本内容: The best food in the galaxy, hands down.
翻译内容: 银河系最好的食物，唾手可得。

文本内容: The best combination of oily, garlicky, and crusty known to mothkind.
翻译内容: 这是蛾族已知的油、蒜和其他有壳的玩意的最佳组合。

文本内容: Some good down-home country-style, rootin'-tootin', revolver-shootin', dad-gum yeehaw cornbread.
A chunk of crispy, cowboy-style cornbread. Consume contentedly.
翻译内容: 一块脆脆的牛仔式玉米面包，心满意足的消费。

文本内容: Ælorölen (cheese balls) are a traditional mothic dessert, made of soft cheese, powdered sugar and flour, rolled into balls, battered and then deep fried. They're often served with either chocolate sauce or honey, or sometimes both!
A light and fluffy vegan marshmallow flavoured with vanilla and rum and topped with soft chocolate. These are known to the moths as höllflöfstarkken: cloud squares.
Fluffy little clouds of joy- in a strangely moth-like colour.
翻译内容: 毛茸茸的快乐小云朵——有着奇怪的蛾一般的颜色。

文本内容: Red porridge with yoghurt. The name and vegetable ingredients obscure the sweet nature of the dish, which is commonly served as a dessert aboard the fleet.
A rubbery strip of gum. It's stamped with the emblem of the Mothic Nomad Fleet.
翻译内容: 一种橡胶状的口香糖。上面印着蛾族游牧舰队的标志。

文本内容: Stay awake during long shifts in the maintenance tunnels with Activin! The approval seal of the Mothic Nomad Fleet is emblazoned on the packaging, alongside a litany of health and safety disclaimers in both Mothic and Galactic Common.
翻译内容: 使用活化素在维护管道长时间的轮班中保持清醒！包装上装饰着飞蛾游牧舰队的批准印章，旁边是一长串蛾族和银河共同体的健康和安全免责声明。

文本内容: Spacer's Sidekick: Breathe easy with a friend at your side!
翻译内容: 太空老友：有朋友在你身边呢，尽管放心!

文本内容: A fluffy pancake. The softer, superior relative of the waffle.
翻译内容: 蓬松的薄饼。华夫饼更柔软的长辈。

文本内容: A barely cooked mess that some may mistake for a pancake. It longs for the griddle.
翻译内容: 一种几乎没有煮熟的食物，有些人可能会误认为是煎饼。它渴望得到煎锅。

文本内容: A fluffy and delicious blueberry pancake.
A fluffy and delicious chocolate chip pancake.
翻译内容: 一块松软可口的巧克力碎片松饼.

文本内容: A fat stack of fluffy pancakes!
A grand tower of fluffy, delicious pancakes!
翻译内容: 一个由蓬松美味的煎饼组成的宏伟高塔！

文本内容: A massive towering spire of fluffy, delicious pancakes. It looks like it could tumble over!
翻译内容: 松软可口的煎饼堆成的巨大尖顶，它看起来好像要倒了！

文本内容: A delicious and spongy little cake.
A delicious and spongy little cake, with berries.
翻译内容: 美味而松软的小蛋糕，点缀有浆果

文本内容: My stomach is a graveyard! No living being can quench my bloodthirst!
A delicious and spongy little cake.
A true prophecy in each cookie!
翻译内容: 每个饼干都有一个真实的预言！

文本内容: This is a finely-prepared plump helmet biscuit. The ingredients are exceptionally minced plump helmet, and well-minced dwarven wheat flour.
Microwave is taken by a fey mood! It has cooked an exceptional plump helmet biscuit!
Just like your little sister used to make.
翻译内容: 就像你从前的妹妹会做的饼干.

文本内容: A sugar cookie in the shape of a [shape]. I hope Santa likes it!
Which side's the head, the fat end or the thin end?
翻译内容: 哪一边是头，是粗的那一边还是细的那一边？

文本内容: The best of both cookie and oat.
翻译内容: 饼干和燕麦都是最好的。

文本内容: Why would you put raisins on a cookie?
翻译内容: 你为什么要在饼干上放葡萄干？

文本内容: A sweet cupcake with cherry bits.
Blue cherries inside a delicious cupcake.
翻译内容: 美味的纸杯蛋糕里有蓝色的樱桃。

文本内容: A sticky pastry bun glazed with honey.
翻译内容: 一个粘糊糊的裹满蜂蜜的圆面包。

文本内容: A sicilian treat that makes you into a wise guy.
翻译内容: 西西里岛的款待能让你变聪颖。

文本内容: Delicious waffle cone, but no ice cream.
翻译内容: 美味的华夫卷筒，这个蛋筒可没有冰淇淋。

文本内容: Delicious chocolate cone, but no ice cream.
翻译内容: 美味的巧克力锥形蛋卷筒，但上面没有冰淇淋。

文本内容: A tasty, chewy peanut butter cookie.
翻译内容: 美味又有嚼劲的花生曲奇。

文本内容: A sticky mixture of raw brownie batter, cook it in the oven!
翻译内容: 生布朗尼面糊的粘稠混合物，放在烤箱里烤!

文本内容: An uncut sheet of cooked brownie, use a knife to cut it!.
翻译内容: 一块没切开的布朗尼蛋糕，用刀切！

文本内容: A square slice of delicious, chewy brownie. Often the target of potheads.
翻译内容: 一块方形的美味、耐嚼的布朗尼。通常是瘾君子的目标。
一个简单的馅饼，但不影响它的美味。

文本内容: Just like back home, on clown planet! HONK!
翻译内容: 就像回到家一样，在小丑星球上！嘟嘟！

文本内容: No black birds, this is a good sign.
翻译内容: 没有黑鸟，这是一个好迹象。

文本内容: No brown bears, this is a good sign.
翻译内容: 没有棕熊,倒是个好兆头.

文本内容: An old barber recipe, very delicious!
翻译内容: 来自一个老理发师的食谱，非常美味!

文本内容: I bet you love stuff made out of plump helmets!
翻译内容: 我敢说你喜欢膨头菇做的东西！

文本内容: Microwave is taken by a fey mood! It has cooked an exceptional plump pie!
翻译内容: 微波炉被一种超自然的波动吸引了！它做了一个非凡的膨头菇的馅饼!
美味的肉馅饼。很可能是异端。

文本内容: A pie containing sweet sweet love...or apple.
翻译内容: 这个馅饼里面含有甜甜的爱……或苹果。

文本内容: Taste so good, make a grown man cry.
翻译内容: 味道是如此的好，能让一个成年人哭。

文本内容: A delicious treat for the autumn months.
A slice of pumpkin pie, with whipped cream on top. Perfection.
翻译内容: 一片南瓜馅饼，上面放着生奶油。完美

文本内容: A tasty dessert that won't make it through a metal detector.
翻译内容: 一种美味的甜点，无法通过金属探测器。

文本内容: A tasty dessert that reminds you of the wine you didn't make.

翻译内容: 特制的低温手榴弹，启动后迅速冷却内容物。

翻译内容: 启动后，它能迅速冷却100 K，飞溅范围比普通型号的外壳小。

文本内容: Upon ignition, it rapidly heats contents by 500 K.
翻译内容: 启动后，它能迅速加热500 K。

文本内容: A custom made advanced release grenade. It is able to be detonated more than once. Can be configured using a multitool.
This casing is able to detonate more than once. Can be configured using a multitool.
Used for emergency sealing of hull breaches.
翻译内容: 用于船体缺口的紧急密封。

文本内容: Used for emergency sealing of hull breaches, while keeping areas accessible.
翻译内容: 用于紧急密封船体缺口，同时保持区域可通行。

文本内容: Used for clearing rooms of living things.
翻译内容: 用来清理房间里的活着的东西。

文本内容: Used for purging large areas of invasive plant species. Contents under pressure. Do not directly inhale contents.
翻译内容: 用于清除大面积的入侵植物，内容物经过压缩，可别直接吸入它。

文本内容: BLAM!-brand foaming space cleaner. In a special applicator for rapid cleaning of wide areas.
Waffle Co.-brand foaming space cleaner. In a special applicator for rapid cleaning of wide areas.
Used for nonlethal riot control. Contents under pressure. Do not directly inhale contents.
翻译内容: 用于非致命地控制暴乱，内容物经过压缩，可别直接吸入它

文本内容: Used for wide scale painting projects.

翻译内容: 你应该看不到这个描述。
为了那火辣而华丽的外表。
为了那冷酷而华丽的外表。

文本内容: BURN!-brand foaming clf3. In a special applicator for rapid purging of wide areas.
翻译内容: 焚烧！牌发泡三氟化氯。作为大面积快速清除的专用手段。

文本内容: Tiger Cooperative chemical foam grenade. Causes temporary irration, blindness, confusion, mutism, and mutations to carbon based life forms. Contains additional spore toxin.
翻译内容: 老虎合作社化学泡沫手榴弹。导致暂时的愤怒、失明、混乱、失声和碳基生命形式的突变。含有额外的孢子毒素。

文本内容: WARNING: GRENADE WILL RELEASE DEADLY SPORES CONTAINING ACTIVE AGENTS. SEAL SUIT AND AIRFLOW BEFORE USE.
翻译内容: 警告：手榴弹会释放含有活性物质的致命孢子。使用前确保套装和呼吸装置完全密封。

文本内容: A vessel of concentrated religious might.
翻译内容: 汇聚了宗教力量的容器。

文本内容: Use of this weapon may constitute a war crime in your area, consult your local captain.
翻译内容: 在你所在的地区使用这种武器可能构成战争罪，请咨询当地舰长。

文本内容: A smaller segment of a clusterbang. Better run!
It is designed to wreak havoc on electronic systems.
翻译内容: 它的目的是破坏电子系统。

文本内容: A little stick coated with metal powder and barium nitrate, burns with a pleasing sparkle.
翻译内容: 一根涂有金属粉末和硝酸钡的小棍子，燃烧时发出令人愉快的火花

文本内容: Outlawed in most of the sector. Doubles as an excellent finger remover.
翻译内容: 在大部分地区被视为非法物品，非常擅长移除手指

文本内容: A grenade that generates more shrapnel the more you rotate it in your hand after pulling the pin. This one releases shrapnel shards.
A grenade that generates more shrapnel the more you rotate it in your hand after pulling the pin. This one releases stingballs.

翻译内容: 一种不牢靠的简易燃烧装置。

文本内容: A modified flashbang which uses hypnotic flashes and mind-altering soundwaves to induce an instant trance upon detonation.
翻译内容: 一种改进的闪光弹，它使用催眠闪光和改变思维的声波，在爆炸时引发瞬间恍惚。

翻译内容: 用于在特定区域打洞，却不造成太多额外的洞。破坏者的最爱。

文本内容: A shaped high-explosive breaching charge. Designed to ensure user safety and wall nonsafety.
翻译内容: 一种成型的高爆破甲炸药。旨在确保用户安全和墙壁不安全。

文本内容: Real bruh moment if you ever see this. Probably tell a c*der or something.
The word '[pick(bruh_moment)]' is scribbled on it in crayon.
It will unleash an unspecified anomaly in the surrounding vicinity.
翻译内容: 它会在周围释放一个未知异常。

文本内容: The label reads: \"WARNING: DEVICE WILL RELEASE LIVE SPECIMENS UPON ACTIVATION. SEAL SUIT BEFORE USE.\" It is warm to the touch and vibrates faintly.
翻译内容: 标签上写着: \"警告：激活后, 设备会释放活体样本. 使用前请密封套装. \"它摸起来暖和与在轻微振动.

文本内容: A sleek device often given to clowns on their 10th birthdays for protection. You can hear faint scratching coming from within.

A sleek device often given to clowns on their 10th birthdays for protection. While a typical C.L.U.W.N.E only holds one creature, sometimes foolish young clowns try to cram more in, often to disasterous effect.
A syndicate manufactured explosive used to sow destruction and chaos.
翻译内容: 一个辛迪加制造的炸药，用来制造破坏和混乱。

文本内容: A compact shrapnel grenade meant to devastate nearby organisms and cause some damage in the process. Pull pin and throw opposite direction.
翻译内容: 一枚小型破片榴弹旨在摧毁附近的生物，并在这一过程中造成一些损害。拉动插销并朝相反方向抛出。

文本内容: An anti-personnel fragmentation grenade, this weapon excels at killing soft targets by shredding them with metal shrapnel.
An anti-everything fragmentation grenade, this weapon excels at killing anything any everything by shredding them with metal shrapnel.

An advanced grenade that releases a harmful stream of gluons inducing radiation in those nearby. These gluon streams will also make victims feel exhausted, and induce shivering. This extreme coldness will also likely wet any nearby floors.

翻译内容: 它有一个可调节的定时器。

翻译内容: 使用强大的蓝空接地技术来剥夺植入物受体的传送(与被传送)能力. 曾被严厉的奴隶主(与一些特别严格的老板)用于以防他们的奴隶使用传送脱离控制.

翻译内容: 一个用于植入'自由'植入物的辛迪加植入器

翻译内容: -是你吗，上帝?-是我，辛迪加特工

翻译内容: 一个用于植入'内置无线电'植入物的辛迪加植入器

翻译内容: 允许你在醒目的地方隐藏。

翻译内容: 给予一个最多可以存放两件大物品的蓝空口袋。

翻译内容: 一个用于植入'储存'植入物的辛迪加植入器

文本内容: A wooden truncheon for beating criminal scum. Left click to stun, right click to harm.
翻译内容: 用于殴打犯罪渣滓的木制警棍。左键点击眩晕，右键点击伤害。

翻译内容: 一个奇怪的盒子，里面装着木工工具和一张把电击棒变成别的什么东西的说明书。

翻译内容: 一种紧凑而强力的个人自卫武器。折叠时可以隐藏。

翻译内容: 分配给辛迪加承包商的一种紧凑的特化指挥棒，目标施加轻微电击。

翻译内容: 一根使人丧失能力的击晕棒。左键点击眩晕，右键点击伤害。

翻译内容: 一根临时制作的电棍，左键点击眩晕，右键点击伤害

文本内容: A device invented in 2486 for the great Space Emu War by the confederacy of Australicus, these high-tech boomerangs also work exceptionally well at stunning crewmembers. Just be careful to catch it when thrown!
A prod with a bluespace crystal on the end. The crystal doesn't look too fun to touch.
翻译内容: 末端有蓝空水晶的棒，触碰这颗水晶看起来可不是个好点子。

文本内容: May the force be within you.
For heavy duty cutting. It has a carbon-fiber blade in addition to a toggleable hard-light edge to dramatically increase sharpness.
翻译内容: 用于重型切割。它有一个碳纤维刀片，此外还有一个可开关的激光刀刃，可显著提升锐度。

文本内容: A concentrated beam of energy in the shape of a blade. Very stylish... and lethal.
翻译内容: 叶片形状的集中能量束，非常时尚…和致命。

文本内容: An extremely sharp blade made out of hard light. Packs quite a punch.
翻译内容: 由硬光制成的极锋利的刀片，相当有冲击力。

文本内容: A tool used by great men to placate the frothing masses.
翻译内容: 伟人用来安抚愤怒群众的工具。

文本内容: A grotesque blade that on closer inspection seems to be made out of synthetic flesh, it still feels like it would hurt very badly as a weapon.
翻译内容: 这把奇形怪状的刀，仔细一看，似乎是由人造肉制成的，但作为武器，它仍然可以让人体验到痛苦。

文本内容: An elegant weapon, its monomolecular edge is capable of cutting through flesh and bone with ease.
翻译内容: 这是一种优雅的武器，它的单分子边缘能够轻松切割肉和骨。

文本内容: Taken from a giant bee and folded over one thousand times in pure honey. Can sting through anything.
翻译内容: 取自一只大蜜蜂，在纯蜂蜜中浸渍了一千多次。可以刺穿任何东西。

文本内容: In a station full of bad ideas, this might just be the worst.
翻译内容: 在一个充斥着坏主意的空间站里，这可能是最糟糕的。

文本内容: Somewhat eccentric and outdated, it still stings like hell to be hit by.
翻译内容: 有些古怪和过时，但被它打中仍然像地狱一样刺痛人。

文本内容: A telescopic roasting stick with a miniature shield generator designed to ensure entry into various high-tech shielded cooking ovens and firepits.
翻译内容: 一种带微型屏障发生器的伸缩烤棒，被设计用于确保进入各种高科技屏障防护的烹饪炉和火坑时候的安全。

文本内容: [held_sausage.desc] It has been cooked to perfection on \a [target].
The grandson of the club, yet the grandfather of the baseball bat. Most notably used by holy orders in days past.
翻译内容: 这是棍棒的孙子，也是棒球棒的祖父，最著名那一部分为曾经的圣职人员使用。

文本内容:
A highly illegal, highly dangerous upgrade for artificial intelligence units, granting them a variety of powers as well as the ability to hack APCs.
This upgrade does not override any active laws, and must be applied directly to an active AI core.
An illegal software package that will allow an artificial intelligence to 'hear' from its cameras via lip reading and hidden microphones.
翻译内容: 这是一个非法软件包，可以让人工智能通过读唇和隐藏麦克风‘听到’摄像头周围的声音。

文本内容: A complex metal backbone with standard limb sockets and pseudomuscle anchors.
翻译内容: 一种复杂的金属脊柱，带有标准的肢体插座和假肌肉锚。

文本内容: Used to cool a mounted disabler, increasing the potential current in it and thus its recharge rate.
An energy-operated thruster system for cyborgs.
翻译内容: 用于赛博格的能量驱动推进器系统。
采矿用赛博格钻石钻机

文本内容: A diamond drill replacement for the mining model's standard drill.
翻译内容: 用钻石钻头取代了标准钻头的采矿模块。

文本内容: A satchel of holding replacement for mining cyborg's ore satchel module.
翻译内容: 用蓝空矿石袋取代采矿赛博的矿石袋模块。

文本内容: janitor cyborg trash bag of holding
A trash bag of holding replacement for the janiborg's standard trash bag.
翻译内容: 用蓝空垃圾袋取代清洁赛博的标准垃圾袋。

文本内容: An advanced mop replacement for the janiborg's standard mop.
翻译内容: 一种替代了清洁博格标准拖把的先进拖把。
清洁工赛博格电镀修理工具

文本内容: A tiny heating device to repair burnt and damaged hull platings with.
翻译内容: 一种小型加热装置，用于修复烧焦和损坏的船体板。

文本内容: Unlocks the hidden, deadlier functions of a cyborg.
翻译内容: 解锁赛博格隐藏的致命功能。
矿用赛博格防熔岩底盘

文本内容: An upgrade kit to apply specialized coolant systems and insulation layers to a mining cyborg's chassis, enabling them to withstand exposure to molten rock.
翻译内容: 一个升级套件，将专用冷却系统和绝缘层应用于采矿赛博格的底盘，使其能够承受暴露的熔岩。

文本内容: This module will repair the cyborg over time.
翻译内容: 该模块将随着时间的推移修复赛博格
医用赛博格先进无针注射器合成器
医用赛博格手术处理器

文本内容: Bluespace Optimized Remote Intelligence Synchronization. An uplink device which takes the place of an MMI in cyborg endoskeletons, creating a robotic shell controlled by an AI.
A cyborg resizer, it makes a cyborg huge.
翻译内容: 一个赛博格大小调整器，它使一个赛博格变得巨大。
工程赛博格快速零件交换器

文本内容: A rapid part exchange device for the engineering cyborg.
翻译内容: 一种用于工程赛博格的快速零件交换装置。

翻译内容: 医疗赛博格的船员定位模块。允许远程访问船员监控仪。

文本内容: Allows you to to turn a cyborg into a standard cyborg.
翻译内容: 允许您将一个赛博格转换为标准型赛博格。

文本内容: Allows you to to turn a cyborg into a clown, honk.
翻译内容: 允许您将一个赛博格转换为小丑博格，嘟嘟

文本内容: An engineering cyborg upgrade allowing for manipulation of circuit boards.
翻译内容: 一种工程赛博格升级，允许使其操作电路板。

文本内容: A supplementary beaker storage apparatus for medical cyborgs.
翻译内容: 一种用于医疗赛博格的辅助烧杯存储设备。

文本内容: An experimental push broom used for efficiently pushing refuse.
翻译内容: 一种实验性长柄扫帚，用于高效地推扫垃圾。

翻译内容: 一种可重复使用的固件重置工具，可以强制重新启动已停机但已修复的赛博格，使其重新联机。

翻译内容: 奖励人类各种零食。可以在分配模式和高速喷射模式之间切换。

噢，不！一个高速移动的棒棒糖！

文本内容: For when a someone really needs a hug.
翻译内容: 当一个人真的需要拥抱的时候很有用。

文本内容: Releases a harmless blast that confuses most organics. For when the harm is JUST TOO MUCH.
An advanced chemical synthesizer and injection system, designed for heavy-duty medical equipment.
翻译内容: 一种先进的化学合成和注射系统，专为重型医疗设备设计。

文本内容: Keeps the crew happy and productive!
Keeps the crew so happy they don't work!
翻译内容: 让船员们开心到不工作！
辛迪加赛博格无针注射器

文本内容: An advanced drink synthesizer and mixer.
翻译内容: 高级饮料合成器和混合器。

文本内容: Will mix drinks that knock them dead.
翻译内容: 可以混合饮料，使他们不省人事
此设备似乎无法正常工作。

文本内容: A special apparatus for carrying beakers without spilling the contents.
翻译内容: 一种特殊的设备，用于携带烧杯而不会溢出内容物。
一种补充烧杯存储的装置。

文本内容: A special apparatus for carrying drinks without spilling the contents. Will resynthesize any drinks you pour out!
翻译内容: 盛饮料的特殊装置，用来盛饮料而不把里面的东西洒出来，会重新合成你倒出来的任何饮料!

文本内容: A container for holding body parts.
A special apparatus for carrying and manipulating circuit boards.
翻译内容: 用来搬运和操纵电路板的特殊装置。

文本内容: A tiny heating device that's powered by a cyborg's excess heat. Its intended purpose is to repair burnt or damaged hull platings, but it can also be used as a crude lighter or cautery.
翻译内容: 一个由半机械人多余热量提供能量的微型加热装置，它为是修复烧焦或损坏的船体镀板而设计，但它也可以用作简陋的打火机或烧灼器。

文本内容: A device that projects a dampening field that weakens kinetic energy above a certain threshold. Projects a field that drains power per second while active, that will weaken and slow damaging projectiles inside its field. Still being a prototype, it tends to induce a charge on ungrounded metallic surfaces.
A glowing bluespace crystal, not much is known about how they work. It looks very delicate.
翻译内容: 一块发光的蓝空晶体，其工作原理尚不清楚。它看起来很精致。

文本内容: An artificially made bluespace crystal, it looks delicate.
翻译内容: 一块人工制作的蓝空水晶，看起来很精致。

文本内容: A stable polycrystal, made of fused-together bluespace crystals. You could probably break one off.
翻译内容: 一种稳定的多晶，由融合在一起的蓝色空间晶体组成，你可能要取一个下来。

文本内容: It's worth [total_worth] credit[(total_worth > 1) ? "s" : null] in total.
Instead of a license plate number, this could contain a quote like \"Live laugh love\".
A therapeutic gel pack and bandages designed to treat blunt-force trauma.
翻译内容: 含有治疗性凝胶和绷带，用于治疗物理性外伤。

文本内容: A roll of elastic cloth, perfect for stabilizing all kinds of wounds, from cuts and burns, to broken bones.
翻译内容: 一卷弹性纱布，非常适合稳定各种伤口，从割伤、烧伤到骨折。

文本内容: A roll of elastic cloth, perfect for stabilizing all kinds of slashes, punctures and burns.
翻译内容: 一卷弹性纱布，非常适合稳定各种外伤，从割伤到刺伤。

文本内容: A roll of cloth roughly cut from something that does a decent job of stabilizing wounds, but less efficiently so than real medical gauze.
翻译内容: 从某种东西上撕下的一卷布，可以很好地稳定伤口，但效果不如真正的医用纱布。

文本内容: Basic sterile sutures used to seal up cuts and lacerations and stop bleeding.
翻译内容: 普通的无菌缝合线，用于缝合割伤和撕裂伤并止血。

文本内容: A value pack of cheap sutures, not very good at repairing damage, but still decent at stopping bleeding.
翻译内容: 一种超值套装里面的廉价缝针，不太擅长修复损伤，但在止血方面仍然不错

文本内容: A suture infused with drugs that speed up wound healing of the treated laceration.
翻译内容: 一种注入药物的缝合线，可以加速治疗伤口的愈合

文本内容: Basic burn ointment, rated effective for second degree burns with proper bandaging, though it's still an effective stabilizer for worse burns. Not terribly good at outright healing burns though.
翻译内容: 基础的烫伤药膏，对经适当包扎的二度烫伤有效，但他依然对灾难性烧伤有一定稳定作用，不过，在彻底治愈烧伤方面并不是很在行

文本内容: A bacteriostatic mesh used to dress burns.
翻译内容: 用来包扎烧伤处的抑菌网

文本内容: An advanced mesh made with aloe extracts and sterilizing chemicals, used to treat burns.
翻译内容: 一种先进的网状物，由芦荟提取物和杀菌化学品制成，用于治疗烧伤

文本内容: A healing paste for minor cuts and burns.
翻译内容: 用于小伤口和烧伤的愈合膏

文本内容: A potent medical gel that, when applied to a damaged bone in a proper surgical setting, triggers an intense melding reaction to repair the wound. Can be directly applied alongside surgical sticky tape to a broken bone in dire circumstances, though this is very harmful to the patient and not recommended.
翻译内容: 一种强效医用凝胶，在适当的手术环境下应用于受损骨骼时，会引发强烈的融合反应以修复伤口。在极其严重的情况下，可与手术胶带一起直接用于骨折，尽管这对患者非常有害，不推荐使用。

文本内容: A type of primitive herbal poultice.\nWhile traditionally used to prepare corpses for the mourning feast, it can also treat scrapes and burns on the living, however, it is liable to cause shortness of breath when employed in this manner.\nIt is imbued with ancient wisdom.
翻译内容: 一种原始的药草膏药\n虽然传统上用于准备哀悼宴会所需的尸体，但它也可以治疗生者身上的擦伤和烧伤，然而，如果以这种方式使用，它很容易导致患者呼吸急促\n它充满了古老的智慧

文本内容: Some rods. Can be used for building or something.
翻译内容: 一些铁制成的棒子，可用于建筑或其他用途

文本内容: Treated, specialized iron rods. When exposed to the vaccum of space their coating breaks off, but they can hold up against the extreme heat of active lava.
翻译内容: 经过处理的专用铁棒。当暴露在真空中时，它们的涂层会开裂，但它们可以抵抗熔岩的极端高温

文本内容: Used for sticking to things for sticking said things to people.
翻译内容: 用来黏住东西，或者堵上别人的嘴

文本内容: Quite possibly the most mischevious substance in the galaxy. Use with extreme lack of caution.
翻译内容: 很可能是银河系中最黏的物质。使用时要极度小心.

文本内容: Used for sticking to things for sticking said things inside people.
翻译内容: 用来黏住东西，或者让别人自作自受

文本内容: You didn't know tape could look so sinister. Welcome to Space Station 13.
翻译内容: 你没想到世界上居然还能有这么危险的胶带，欢迎来到十三号太空站

文本内容: Made for patching broken bones back together alongside bone gel, not for playing pranks.

文本内容: It seems to be pulsing with suspiciously enticing energies.

文本内容: Wow! With enough of these, you could buy a bike! ...Pssh, yeah right.

文本内容: \"This is a plaque in honour of our comrades on the G4407 Stations. Hopefully TG4407 model can live up to your fame and fortune.\" Scratched in beneath that is a crude image of a meteor and a spaceman. The spaceman is laughing. The meteor is exploding.
翻译内容: \"这是为纪念G4407站的同志们而立的牌匾，希望TG4407型号不负您的声望与财富。\"在这幅画的下方是一颗陨石和一名宇航员的粗糙图像，宇航员微笑着，陨石在他背后爆散成碎片。

文本内容: WARNING: These devices are extremely dangerous and can cause blindness and skin irritation.
翻译内容: 警告：这些设备极其危险，可能导致失明与刺激皮肤.
一个装有5枚电磁脉冲手榴弹的盒子

文本内容: Box full of scum-bag tracking utensils.
翻译内容: 装满追踪渣滓用具的盒子。

文本内容: For finding those who have died on the accursed lavaworld.
翻译内容: 为了找到那些死在受诅咒的拉瓦兰大陆上的人。
盒装'遥控化合物'植入物套件

文本内容: Box of stuff used to implant chemicals.
翻译内容: 一盒用于植入化学品的植入物。

文本内容: Box of exile implants. It has a picture of a clown being booted through the Gateway.
翻译内容: 一盒放逐植入物。上面有一张小丑被踢出大门的照片

文本内容: Take away their last shred of dignity, their name.
翻译内容: 夺走他们最后的尊严，他们的名字。

文本内容: A box full of PDA cartridges used by Security.
A box full of standard firing pins, to allow newly-developed firearms to operate.
翻译内容: 一个装满标准撞针的盒子, 使新开发枪械能被使用

文本内容: A box full of paywall firing pins, to allow newly-developed firearms to operate behind a custom-set paywall.
box of laser tag firing pins
A box full of laser tag firing pins, to allow newly-developed firearms to require wearing brightly coloured plastic armor before being able to be used.
A box full of rubber shots, designed for riot shotguns.
翻译内容: 一个装满橡胶霰弹的盒子，专为防暴霰弹枪设计。

文本内容: A box full of lethal shots, designed for riot shotguns.
翻译内容: 装满致命霰弹的盒子，专为防暴霰弹枪设计。

文本内容: A box full of beanbag shells.
翻译内容: 一个装满豆袋弹的盒子。

文本内容: Contains several grenades used to rapidly purge heresy.
翻译内容: 包含几枚用于快速清除异端的手榴弹。

文本内容: This box has a small label on it stating that it's from the Gorlex Marauders. Contains an assortment of \"fireworks\".
翻译内容: 这个盒子上有一个小标签，上面写着它来自Gorlex掠夺者，包含各种\"烟火\"。

文本内容: A box filled with illegal firecrackers. You wonder who still makes these.
翻译内容: 装满非法爆竹的盒子。你想知道谁还在做这些。

文本内容: A box of Nanotrasen brand sparklers, burns hot even in the cold of space-winter.
翻译内容: 一盒纳米传讯品牌的烟花棒，即使在太空冬天的寒冷中也会燃烧起来。

文本内容: It has a picture of drinking glasses on it.
翻译内容: 它上面有一张酒杯的照片。

文本内容: It has pictures of paper cups on the front.
A box of spare PDA microcomputers.

翻译内容: 一盒 害-必-滚 捕鼠器

文本内容: Keep out of reach of children.
翻译内容: 放在儿童无法接触的地方。

文本内容: Eight wrappers of fun! Ages 8 and up. Not suitable for children.
翻译内容: 八包好玩的东西！适合8岁及以上的人群，不适合儿童使用。

文本内容: A small box of Almost But Not Quite Plasma Premium Matches.
翻译内容: 一小盒几乎但不完全是优质的等离子火柴。

文本内容: This box is shaped on the inside so that only light tubes and bulbs fit.
翻译内容: 这个盒子的内衬是灯泡状的，所以只有灯管和灯泡才放的进去。

文本内容: Contains everything you need to build your own Dish Drive!
翻译内容: 包含您需要的一切，以建立您自己的碟片驱动！

文本内容: The latest set of collectable action figures.
翻译内容: 最新一组可收藏的活动人偶。

文本内容: pin the tail on the corgi supplies
For ages 10 and up. ...Why is this even on a space station? Aren't you a little old for babby games?
翻译内容: 适用于10岁及以上的人群……为什么这会出现在空间站上？你玩婴儿游戏是不是有点太老了？

文本内容: A tank of compressed gas for use as propulsion in zero-gravity areas. Use with caution.
翻译内容: 在零重力区域用作推进装置的压缩气罐。谨慎使用

文本内容: A jetpack made from two air tanks, a fire extinguisher and some atmospherics equipment. It doesn't look like it can hold much.
翻译内容: 由两个气罐、一个灭火器和一些大气设备制成的喷射背包。看起来它装不下多少东西。

文本内容: It works well in a void.
翻译内容: 它能在真空中正常工作。

文本内容: A tank of compressed oxygen for use as propulsion in zero-gravity areas. Use with caution.
翻译内容: 在零重力区域用作推进装置的压缩氧气罐。谨慎使用

文本内容: A lightweight tactical harness, used by those who don't want to be weighed down by traditional jetpacks.
翻译内容: 一种轻便的战术背带，供那些不想被传统喷气背包拖累的人使用。

文本内容: A compact, lightweight jetpack containing a high amount of compressed oxygen.
翻译内容: 一种结构紧凑、重量轻、含有大量压缩氧气的喷射背包。

文本内容: A tank of compressed oxygen for use as propulsion in zero-gravity areas by security forces.
翻译内容: 安全部队在零重力区域用作推进装置的压缩氧气罐。

文本内容: A tank of compressed carbon dioxide for use as propulsion in zero-gravity areas. Painted black to indicate that it should not be used as a source for internals.
翻译内容: 在零重力区域用作推进装置的压缩二氧化碳气罐。涂成黑色，表明不应将其用作呼吸用的气源。

文本内容: A tank of oxygen, this one is blue.
翻译内容: 装有氧气的罐体。颜色为蓝色。

文本内容: A tank of oxygen, this one is yellow.
翻译内容: 装有氧气的罐体。颜色为黄色。

文本内容: A tank of oxygen, this one is red.
翻译内容: 装有氧气的罐体。颜色为红色。

文本内容: A tank with an N2O/O2 gas mix.
翻译内容: 装有一氧化二氮（N2O）与氧气（O2）的混合气体的罐体。

文本内容: Contains dangerous plasma. Do not inhale. Warning: extremely flammable.
翻译内容: 含有危险等离子体。不要吸入。警告：极易燃。

文本内容: A tank of plasma gas designed specifically for use as internals, particularly for plasma-based lifeforms. If you're not a Plasmaman, you probably shouldn't use this.
翻译内容: 专门设计用作呼吸用的等离子气罐，特别是用于等离子生命体。如果你不是等离子人，你很可能不应该使用这个。

文本内容: Used for emergencies. Contains very little oxygen, so try to conserve it until you actually need it.
翻译内容: 用于紧急情况。装有极少量氧气，所以，不到万不得已，尽量不要使用。

文本内容: A generic tank used for storing and transporting gasses. Can be used for internals.
翻译内容: 用于储存和运输气体的普通气罐。可用作呼吸气源。

文本内容: A S.U.N.S.H.I.N.E. brand watertank backpack with nozzle to water plants.
A mister nozzle attached to a water tank.
翻译内容: 连接在水箱上的喷雾嘴。

文本内容: A janitorial cleaner backpack with nozzle to clean blood and graffiti.
翻译内容: 一个清洁背包，带有可以清洁血迹和涂鸦的喷嘴。

文本内容: A janitorial spray nozzle attached to a watertank, designed to clean up large messes.
翻译内容: 安装在水箱上的清洁喷嘴，用于清理大面积污物。
叛徒-捆绑者-2500型镇压背包

文本内容: The ultimate crowd-control device; this tool allows the user to quickly and efficiently pacify groups of hostile targets.
翻译内容: 终极人群控制装置；该工具允许用户快速有效地安抚一群敌对目标。

文本内容: A pacifying spray nozzle attached to a pepperspray tank, designed to silence perps.
翻译内容: 安装在胡椒喷雾罐上的镇压喷嘴，用于镇压罪犯。

文本内容: A refrigerated and pressurized backpack tank with extinguisher nozzle, intended to fight fires. Swaps between extinguisher, resin launcher and a smaller scale resin foamer.
翻译内容: 带有灭火器喷嘴的冷冻和加压背包罐，用于灭火。在灭火器、树脂发射器和较小规模的树脂发泡器之间切换。

文本内容: A heavy duty nozzle attached to a firefighter's backpack tank.
翻译内容: 连接在消防员背式水箱上的重型喷嘴。

文本内容: A compacted ball of expansive resin, used to repair the atmosphere in a room, or seal off breaches.
翻译内容: 一种压缩膨胀树脂球，用于修补房间内的大气泄露或密封破裂处。

文本内容: A chemical autoinjector that can be carried on your back.
翻译内容: 一种可以背在背上的化学自动注射器。

文本内容: Wow, a mint condition coder card! Better tell the Github all about this!
It's the back of a trading card... no peeking!
It's the back of a trading card... no peeking!
翻译内容: 这是一张交易卡的背面……不许偷看！

文本内容: Contains six complete fuckups by the coders. Report this on github please!
Contains six cards of varying rarity from the 2560 Core Set. Collect them all!
Trading Card Pack: Resin Frontier Booster Pack
Contains six cards of varying rarity from the Resin Frontier set. Collect them all!
A TGC flipper, for deciding who gets to go first. Also conveniently acts as a counter, for various purposes.
翻译内容: 一个TGC翻转器，用于决定谁先走，还可以方便地充当计数器，用于各种目的。

文本内容: The perfect way to keep your collection of cards safe and valuable.
翻译内容: 这是保护您的卡片收藏安全和价值的完美方式。

文本内容: Wow, a mint condition coder card! Better tell the Github all about this!
A small crowbar. This handy tool is useful for lots of things, such as prying floor tiles or opening unpowered doors.
翻译内容: 一个小撬棍。这个趁手的工具对很多事情都很有用，比如撬地板砖或打开无动力门。

文本内容: A hard-light crowbar. It appears to pry by itself, without any effort required.
翻译内容: 强光撬棍，它似乎可以自己撬开，不需要你出任何力。

文本内容: It's a big crowbar. It doesn't fit in your pockets, because it's big.
翻译内容: 一把大撬棍，它装不进你的口袋，因为它太大了。

文本内容: It's a bulky crowbar. It almost seems deliberately designed to not be able to fit inside of a backpack.
翻译内容: 这是一个笨重的撬棍。它似乎是被故意设计成不能放在背包里的。

文本内容: It's a big crowbar. It doesn't fit in your pockets, because it's big. It feels oddly heavy..
翻译内容: 一把大撬棍，它装不进你的口袋，因为它太大了。它出奇的沉重...

文本内容: It's an old crowbar. Much larger than the pocket sized ones, carrying a lot more heft. They don't make 'em like they used to.
翻译内容: 这是一根旧撬棍，比口袋大得多，携带的重量要重得多，他们不再像这种旧款式那么造了。

文本内容: A set of jaws of life, compressed through the magic of science.
翻译内容: 一套液压钳, 通过科学的魔力压缩。

文本内容: A pocket sized re-engineered copy of Nanotrasen's standard jaws of life. Can be used to force open airlocks in its crowbar configuration.
翻译内容: 一个口袋大小的纳米传讯标准液压钳的重制品。在撬棍模式中，可用于强制打开气闸。

文本内容: A hydraulic prying tool, simple but powerful.
翻译内容: 液压撬具，简单但功能强大。

文本内容: You can be totally screwy with this.
翻译内容: 你完全可以被这玩意搞疯。

文本内容: A powerful automated screwdriver, designed to be both precise and quick.
翻译内容: 功能强大的自动螺丝刀，设计精确且快速。

文本内容: A standard edition welder provided by Nanotrasen.
翻译内容: 纳米传讯提供的标准版焊机

文本内容: A slightly larger welder with a larger tank.
翻译内容: 稍大一点的焊机，配有大油罐。

文本内容: An advanced welder designed to be used in robotic systems. Custom framework doubles the speed of welding.
翻译内容: 设计用于机器人系统的高级焊机。定制框架使焊接速度加倍。

文本内容: A miniature welder used during emergencies.
翻译内容: 紧急情况下使用的小型焊机。

文本内容: An alien welding tool. Whatever fuel it uses, it never runs out.
翻译内容: 外星焊接工具。不管它用的是什么燃料，它都不会用完。
升级过的工业用焊接工具

文本内容: An upgraded welder based of the industrial welder.
An experimental welder capable of self-fuel generation and less harmful to the eyes.
翻译内容: 一种能够自动产生燃料且对眼睛伤害较小的实验焊机。

文本内容: A tool that is used to scrub the rust thoroughly off walls. Not for hair!
翻译内容: 一种用来彻底刷掉墙上锈迹的工具。不能用来梳头！

文本内容: Extremely sharp wirecutters, made out of a silvery-green metal.
翻译内容: 极其锋利的剪线钳，由银绿色金属制成。

文本内容: Cuts wires with the power of ELECTRICITY. Faster than normal wirecutters.
翻译内容: 用电的力量切断电线。比普通剪线钳更快。

文本内容: A wrench with common uses. Can be found in your hand.
翻译内容: 一个常用的扳手。可以在你的手中找到。

文本内容: A polarized wrench. It causes anything placed between the jaws to turn.
翻译内容: 一把极化扳手，它会使放在夹缝之间的任何东西转动。

文本内容: A medical wrench with common(medical?) uses. Can be found in your hand.
翻译内容: 一个常用的医用扳手。可以在你的手中找到。

文本内容: An advanced robotic wrench, powered by internal hydraulics. Twice as fast as the handheld version.
翻译内容: 一个先进的机械扳手，由内部液压驱动。速度是手持版的两倍。

文本内容: It's like a normal wrench but edgier. Can be found on the battlefield.
翻译内容: 与普通扳手类似，但更加锋利。可在战场上找到。
